tigations%20said.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EAgents%20said%20they%20found%20a%20USB%20stick%20in%20his%20possession%20with%20footage%20showing%20a%20young%20girl%20showering.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EAn%20employee%20working%20on%20a%20Royal%20Caribbean%20cruise%20ship%20has%20been%20arrested%20on%20suspicion%20of%20placing%20secret%20cameras%20inside%20passengers'%20bathrooms%20and%20filming%20them%20without%20their%20knowledge.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20probable%20cause%20affidavit%20by%20the%20Homeland%20Security%20Investigations%2C%20part%20of%20the%20US%20Immigration%20and%20Customs%20Enforcement%2C%20said%20that%20Arvin%20Joseph%20Mirasol%2C%20a%20stateroom%20attendant%20at%20the%20cruise%20line%2C%20was%20in%20possession%20of%20a%20USB%20stick%20containing%20child%20pornography%20and%20videos%20of%20women%20undressing%20in%20bathrooms.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20affidavit%2C%20Mirasol%20admitted%20to%20hiding%20video%20cameras%20in%20passengers'%20bathrooms%20and%20told%20investigators%20that%20he%20would%20masturbate%20while%20watching%20the%20videos.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERoyal%20Caribbean%20notified%20agencies%20including%20Homeland%20Security%20Investigations%20in%20late%20February%20that%20a%20member%20of%20crew%20aboard%20its%20Symphony%20of%20the%20Seas%20vessel%20had%20placed%20a%20camera%20in%20passengers'%20bathrooms%2C%20the%20affidavit%20said.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAgents%20boarded%20the%20ship%20when%20it%20docked%20at%20Port%20Everglades%2C%20Florida%2C%20on%20March%203%20and%20took%20Mirasol's%20devices%20including%20his%20phone%2C%20camera%2C%20and%20USB%20stick%2C%20per%20the%20affidavit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20videos%20they%20found%20on%20the%20USB%20stick%20showed%20a%20girl%2C%20estimated%20to%20be%20around%2010%20years%20old%2C%20undressing%20and%20showering%2C%20the%20affidavit%20said.%20The%20start%20of%20the%20footage%20%26quot%3Bclearly%26quot%3B%20shows%20Mirasol%20placing%20the%20camera%20in%20the%20bathroom%2C%20according%20to%20th