y%2C%20%3Cem%3EMemoirs%20of%20a%20Maverick%3A%20The%20First%20Fifty%20Years%20(1941%20to%201991)%3C%2Fem%3E.%20The%20incident%20relates%20to%20the%20late%20actor%2C%20Peter%20Sellers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMani%20and%20I%20were%20then%20undergraduates%20at%20Cambridge%20University.%20He%20was%20studying%20economics%2C%20I%20was%20studying%20history.%20We%20were%20in%20our%20final%20year.%20Mani%20had%20been%20elected%20secretary%20of%20the%20Cambridge%20Union%2C%20the%20prime%20debating%20society%20of%20the%20university%2C%20where%20future%20British%20prime%20ministers%20had%20spoken%20as%20students.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%2C%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20had%20been%20elected%20president%20of%20the%20Cambridge%20India%20Society%2C%20where%20Indians%20studying%20and%20teaching%20at%20the%20university%20used%20to%20meet.%20My%20job%20was%20also%20to%20invite%20eminent%20speakers%20to%20address%20us%20once%20a%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20a%20challenging%20task%20as%20the%20India%20Society%20had%20been%20in%20the%20red%20for%20many%20years.%20Even%20inviting%20the%20then%20well-known%20editor%20of%20the%20influential%20and%20highly%20respected%20%3Cem%3ENew%20Statesman%20and%20Nation%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20Kingsley%20Martin%2C%20could%20not%20attract%20a%20larger%20paying%20audience%20than%20the%20usual%2030%20or%2040.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECamellia%20Panjabi%2C%20another%20contemporary%2C%20who%20was%20then%20the%20secretary-designate%20of%20the%20India%20Society%2C%20and%20went%20on%20to%20join%20the%20Tata%20Administrative%20Service%20(TAS)%20and%20became%20a%20key%20figure%20in%20the%20expansion%20of%20the%20Taj%20group%20of%20hotels%2C%20said%20one%20day%2C%20%E2%80%9CWhy%20don%E2%80%99t%20you%20try%20and%20get%20Peter%20Sellers%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESellers%20was%20then%20one%20of%20Britain%E2%80%99s%20leading%20comedians%2C%20famous%20for%20a%20popular%20radio%20programme%2C%20called%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Goon%20Show%3C%2Fem%3E.%20He%20had%20starred%20in%20some%20critically%20acclaimed%20British%20films%2C%20including%20the%20classic%20black%20comedy%2C%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Ladykillers%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20in%20which%20Alec%20Guinness%20also%20acted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESellers%2C%20however%2C%20truly%20hit%20big%20time%20internationally%20opposite%20Sophia%20Loren%20in%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Millionairess%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20which%20was%20based%20on%20a%20story%20by%20George%20Bernard%20Shaw%20and%20released%20in%201960.%20He%20played%20the%20role%20of%20an%20Indian%20doctor%2C%20and%20spoke%20in%20what%20was%20considered%20as%20the%20typical%20sing-song%20Indian%20accent.%20As%20a%20result%2C%20many%20of%20my%20English%20university%20friends%20would%20try%20to%20get%20a%20laugh%20by%20conversing%20in%20the%20same%20accent%20when%20talking%20with%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInviting%20Peter%20Sellers%20was%20a%20long%20shot%20but%20I%20decided%20to%20give%20it%20a%20go.%20To%20my%20surprise%2C%20I%20did%20not%20get%20an%20immediate%20%E2%80%9CNo%E2%80%9D%2C%20but%20a%20cautious%20response%20from%20his%20secretary.%20So%2C%20I%20pursued%20the%20matter%20and%20then%2C%20to%20my%20huge%20delight%2C%20she%20told%20me%20that%20he%20had%20agreed%20to%20drive%20down%20from%20London%20to%20Cambridge%20to%20address%20us.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbooks%2Fmani-shankar-aiyar-memoirs%5C%22%3EA%20Profile%20in%20Courage%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20hired%20the%20largest%20hall%20available%2C%20the%20Cambridge%20Union%20building%20where%20it%20held%20its%20debates%20and%20which%20could%20hold%20several%20hundred%20people.%20We%20charged%20a%20small%20entrance%20fee%20of%20two%20shillings%2C%20I%20seem%20to%20recall%20(the%20equivalent%20of%20today%E2%80%99s%20Rs%2010)%2C%20but%20so%20big%20was%20the%20rush%20that%20we%20had%20to%20turn%20quite%20a%20few%20students%20away.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20probably%20the%20biggest%20number%20of%20people%20ever%20to%20attend%20an%20India%20Society%20meeting.%20More%20importantly%2C%20it%20got%20the%20society%20out%20of%20the%20red%2C%20even%20leaving%20behind%20a%20healthy%20balance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20over%20one-and-a-half%20hours%2C%20Sellers%20had%20the%20overflowing%20hall%20in%20splits.%20Being%20the%20wonderful%20mimic%20he%20was%2C%20he%20spoke%20in%20a%20variety%20of%20different%20English%20accents.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOf%20course%2C%20they%20included%20the%20Indian%20one%2C%20but%20the%20French%20as%20well%2C%20which%20he%20would%20use%20to%20marvellous%20effect%20in%20the%20wildly%20successful%20%3Cem%3EPink%20Panther%3C%2Fem%3E%20series%20of%20films%2C%20where%20he%20played%20the%20bumbling%20French%20detective%2C%20Inspector%20Clouseau.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECoincidentally%2C%20when%20Mani%20was%20writing%20his%20memoir%2C%20and%20asked%20me%20if%20I%20could%20remember%20the%20date%20of%20the%20memorable%20Sellers%E2%80%99%20function%2C%20I%20was%20rummaging%20through%20old%20files%20and%20newspaper%20clippings%2C%20trying%20to%20put%20them%20in%20some%20kind%20of%20order.%20And%20there%2C%20I%20found%20my%20university%20diary%20of%201961-62%2C%20and%20a%20yellowed%20clipping%20from%20a%20local%20paper%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3ECambridge%20Daily%20News%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20reporting%20the%20event!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20dated%20June%2012%2C%20so%20clearly%20Sellers%20had%20addressed%20the%20India%20Society%20the%20previous%20evening%20on%20June%2012%2C%201962%2C%20almost%2060%20years%20ago%2C%20a%20virtual%20lifetime%2C%20when%20I%20was%2021.%20I%20even%20found%20the%20brief%20hand-written%20speech%20I%20had%20delivered%20to%20introduce%20Sellers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fpv-narasimha-rao-mani-shankar-aiyar-book-launch%5C%22%3EP.V.%20Narasimha%20Rao%20Was%20%E2%80%98First%20BJP%20PM%E2%80%99%20of%20India%2C%20Says%20Mani%20Shankar%20Aiyar%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20meeting%2C%20Camelia%2C%20Brian%20Pollitt%2C%20a%20close%20friend%20who%20was%20then%20president%20of%20the%20Cambridge%20Union%20(his%20father%2C%20Harry%20Pollitt%2C%20was%20the%20founder%20of%20the%20British%20Communist%20Party)%2C%20Romi%20Khosla%2C%20another%20contemporary%20of%20mine%20at%20Cambridge%20who%20went%20on%20to%20become%20a%20famous%20architect%2C%20and%20I%20took%20Sellers%20out%20for%20dinner%20to%20a%20small%20Indian%20restaurant%20nearby.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20brought%20along%20Mario%20Fabrizi%2C%20an%20actor%20friend.%20At%20the%20dinner%20he%20revealed%20that%20the%20director%20of%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Millionairess%3C%2Fem%3E%20had%20originally%20wanted%20him%20to%20play%20the%20role%20of%20an%20Egyptian%20doctor%2C%20but%20he%20persuaded%20the%20director%20to%20change%20it%20to%20an%20Indian%20doctor%20because%2C%20as%20Sellers%20told%20us%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20had%20got%20to%20know%20many%20Indian%20doctors%20and%20liked%20them%20a%20lot.%E2%80%9D%20He%20also%20made%20a%20startling%20confession.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CDid%20you%20know%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20asked%20us%20rhetorically%2C%20%E2%80%9CThat%20this%20has%20been%20the%20first%20time%20I%20have%20ever%20spoken%20in%20public%3F%20I%20was%20so%20nervous%20at%20the%20prospect%20that%20I%20brought%20Mario%20along%2C%20in%20case%20I%20broke%20down%20and%20could%20not%20continue.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20needn%E2%80%99t%20have%20worried.%20He%20had%20held%20all%20of%20us%20completely%20spellbound%20with%20his%20masterly%20mimicry.%20Sadly%2C%20Sellers%20died%20relatively%20young%2C%20at%20the%20age%20of%2054%2C%20while%20still%20at%20the%20peak%20of%20his%20career.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMani%2C%20thank%20you%20for%20the%20memories.%20And%20we%20are%20all%20looking%20forward%20to%20the%20next%20volume%20of%20your%20memoirs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ERahul%20Singh%20served%20as%20an%20assistant%20editor%20at%20the%20%3C%2Fem%3ETimes%20of%20India%20%3Cem%3Eand%20editor%20at%20the%20%3C%2Fem