ng%20with%20the%20locals%20of%20Raa%20Meedhoo%2C%20the%20President%20highlighted%20that%20the%20area%20of%20sea%20is%20twice%20as%20large%20as%20the%20entire%20land%20mass%20of%20the%20Maldives%20and%20noted%20that%20the%20Maldives%20%26quot%3Bhas%20not%20been%20in%20control%20of%20its%20Exclusive%20Economic%20Zone%20despite%20its%20significantly%20large%20area.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAlthough%20the%20EEZ%20is%20part%20of%20our%20territory%2C%20we%20did%20not%20have%20the%20capacity%20to%20monitor%20the%20area.%20God%20willing%2C%20our%20work%20(to%20monitor%20the%20Maldivian%20waters)%20will%20commence%20in%20March.%20We%20will%20establish%20a%2024X7%20monitoring%20system%20during%20this%20month%2C%26quot%3B%20Sun.mv%2C%20a%20news%20portal%20reported%2C%20quoting%20the%20President.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Maldives%20Coastguard%20currently%20seeks%20regular%20assistance%20from%20the%20militaries%20of%20neighbouring%20countries%2C%20and%20carries%20out%20some%20of%20the%20special%20patrolling%20operations%20with%20foreign%20allies%2C%20the%20news%20portal%20said.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709723340000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2F5nijbjec_chinse-ship_625x300_22_February_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fas-chinese-spy-ship-leaves-maldives-severs-yet-another-pact-with-india-5186771%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Maldives%20will%20not%20renew%20an%20agreement%20with%20India%20to%20conduct%20hydrographic%20surveys%20and%20plans%20to%20acquire%20the%20facilities%20and%20machines%20required%20to%20do%20the%20exercise%20by%20itself%2C%20President%20Mohamed%20Muizzu%20has%20announced.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.c