%20BI%20show.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPaul%20worked%20in%20project%20management%20and%20operated%20businesses%2C%20which%20he%20closed%20at%20the%20pandemic's%20start.%20He%20reactivated%20his%20real%20estate%20license%2C%20but%20he%20began%20gig%20driving%20to%20continue%20providing%20for%20his%2020-%20and%2017-year-old%20kids%20months%20after%20a%20debilitating%20injury.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGig%20companies%2C%20including%20Uber%20and%20Lyft%2C%20have%20said%20they%20are%20committed%20to%20supporting%20drivers%20with%20disabilities%20through%20accessibility%20and%20antidiscrimination%20policies%20and%20resources%20for%20physical%20and%20mental%20disabilities%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20for%20a%20few%20weeks%2C%20he%20worked%2040%20to%2050%20hours%20just%20to%20pay%20for%20his%20rental%20car%20from%20Uber.%20The%20price%20was%20over%20%241%2C500%20last%20November%2C%20and%20he%20said%20he%20lost%20money%20after%20accounting%20for%20expenses%20that%20month.%20Screenshots%20show%20that%20many%20rides%20he%20received%20that%20month%20were%20only%20%242%20to%20%243%2C%20and%20he's%20begun%20to%20decline%20more%20non-profitable%20rides%20across%20the%20different%20platforms.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTrust%20me%2C%20I%20want%20to%20be%20doing%20more%20for%20my%20children%2C%20I%20wish%20I%20could%20be%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Paul%2C%20who%20had%20just%20finished%20nearly%2040%20hours%20of%20driving%20over%20two%20and%20a%20half%20days.%20%26quot%3BThere's%20no%20other%20option%2C%20and%20when%20there's%20no%20one%20else%20to%20turn%20to%2C%20you%20got%20to%20just%20make%20it%20happen.%20It's%20humbling%2C%20and%20it's%20tough.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20older%20parents%20are%20just%20looking%20for%20some%20relief.%20Stormy%2C%2048%2C%20a%20single%20mother%20of%20a%2023-%20and%2020-year-old%2C%20has%20driven%20predominantly%20for%20Uber%20since%202015%20to%20supplement%20her%20Social%20Security%20Disability%20Insurance.%20She%20would%20drive%20at%20night%20after%20her%20kids%20we