n%20November%20is%20far%20starker%20than%20the%20fears%20stoked%20by%20past%20presidents.%20%26quot%3BA%20Trump%20dictatorship%20is%20increasingly%20inevitable%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20recent%20Washington%20Post%20headline%20warned.%20The%20Atlantic%20devoted%20an%20entire%20issue%20to%20the%20authoritarian%20horrors%20in%20store%20for%20America%20%26quot%3BIf%20Trump%20Wins.%26quot%3B%20Every%20four%20years%20or%20so%2C%20Gallup%20asks%20Americans%20ages%2015%20and%20up%3A%20%26quot%3BIdeally%2C%20if%20you%20had%20the%20opportunity%2C%20would%20you%20like%20to%20move%20PERMANENTLY%20to%20another%20country%3F%26quot%3B%20At%20the%20end%20of%20George%20W.%20Bush's%20presidency%2C%20the%20number%20responding%20%26quot%3Byes%26quot%3B%20was%2011%25.%20During%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbarack-obama-michelle-obama-net-worth-2018-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBarack%20Obama's%20tenure%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20it%20was%2010%25.%20During%20Trump's%20presidency%2C%20it%20hit%2016%25.%20That's%20some%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E40%20million%20Americans%20who%20wanted%20to%20leave%20their%20country%20behind%2C%20for%20good.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYoung%20people%20are%20even%20more%20likely%20to%20be%20hopeful%20expats.%20Among%20those%20under%2030%2C%2024%25%20wanted%20to%20leave%20America%20at%20the%20close%20of%20Bush's%20tenure%2C%2018%25%20during%20Obama's%2C%20and%2030%25%20during%20Trump's.%20As%20with%20all%20things%20Trump%2C%20there%20was%20a%20sharp%20gender%20divide%3A%20Only%2020%25%20of%20young%20men%20wanted%20to%20flee%20America%2C%20compared%20to%20a%20whopping%2040%25%20of%20young%20women.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAmericans%20already%20living%20overseas%20are%20bracing%20for%20a%20wave%20of%20new%20expats.%20%26quot%3BThere%20will%20be%20more%20people%20moving%20abroad%20after%20the%20election%20if%20it%20is%20Trump%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Doris%20Speer%2C%20the%20president%20of%20the%20Association%20of%20Americans%20Resident%20Overseas%2C%20a%20nonpartisan%20group%20based%20in%20Paris.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStressing%20that%20she%20was%20expressing%20her%20own%20views%2C%20not%20those%20of%20her%20organization%2C%20Speer%20emphasized%20that%20Trump%20is%20far%20from%20the%20only%20reason%20Americans%20are%20eyeing%20the%20exits.%20That's%20true%3A%20Housing%20prices%20in%20America%20are%20high%2C%20remote%20work%20is%20allowing%20for%20unprecedented%20mobility%2C%20and%20global%20respect%20for%20the%20United%20States%20has%20been%20eroding%20for%20decades%2C%20dating%20back%20to%20the%20war%20in%20Iraq.%20Fewer%20and%20fewer%20Americans%2C%20pollsters%20have%20found%2C%20believe%20%26quot%3Bthe%20American%20Dream%20%E2%80%94%20that%20if%20you%20work%20hard%20you'll%20get%20ahead%20%E2%80%94%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Estill%20holds%20true.%26quot%3B%20In%202012%2C%20it%20was%2053%25.%20By%20October%202023%2C%20it%20was%20down%20to%2036%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20second%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcategory%2Fdonald-trump%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETrump%3C%2Fa%3E%20presidency%2C%20Speer%20said%2C%20could%20serve%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bcatalyst%26quot%3B%20that%20further%20fuels%20the%20growing%20diaspora%20of%20Americans%20living%20in%20exile.%20After%20November%2C%20Europe%20could%20well%20become%20what%20Canada%20was%20for%20draft%20dodgers%20during%20the%20Vietnam%20War%3A%20a%20political%20asylum%20for%20Americans%20fed%20up%20with%20their%20own%20country.%20Call%20them%20Trump's%20Exiles.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20those%20casting%20a%20worried%20eye%20abroad%2C%20the%20economic%20draw%20is%20not%20insignificant.%20When%20I%20was%20looking%20to%20buy%20an%20apartment%20in%20Umbria%2C%20in%20central%20Italy%2C%20I%20found%20that%20prices%20for%20turnkey%20places%20were%20about%20a%20third%20of%20the%20price%20of%20condos%20in%20Sedona%2C%20Arizona.%20Property%20taxes%20and%20homeowners%20insurance%20are%20also%20relatively%20modest%20in%20Italy.%20Gas%20is%20more%20expensive%2C%20but%20the%20mouthwatering%20fare%20at%20local%20restaurants%20%E2%80%94%20wild-boar%20rag%C3%B9%2C%20anyone%3F%20%E2%80%94%20is%20way%20cheaper.%20Politics%20aside%2C%20the%20dollars-and-cents%20pull%20to%20leave%20America%20is%20strong.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20a%20rising%20tide%20of%20conservatism%20at%20home%20is%20clearly%20driving%20more%20Americans%20to%20consider%20a%20move%20abroad.%20The%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fscotus-rules-trump-eligibility-campaign-president-colorado-super-tuesday-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESupreme%20Court's%3C%2Fa%3E%20decision%20to%20overturn%20Roe%20v.%20Wade%20%E2%80%94%20one%20of%20Trump's%20signature%20accomplishments%20%E2%80%94%20has%20aroused%20widespread%20anger%20and%20discontent.%20But%20while%20America%20is%20cracking%20down%20on%20reproductive%20rights%2C%20Europe%20is%20expanding%20them.%20Abortion%20is%20now%20permitted%20in%20nearly%20all%20European%20countries%2C%20including%20Catholic%20countries%20such%20as%20Portugal%2C%20Spain%2C%20and%20Italy.%20Prompted%20by%20tightening%20US%20policies%2C%20France%20just%20enshrined%20the%20right%20to%20abortion%20in%20its%20constitution%20%E2%80%94%20the%20first%20country%20ever%20to%20take%20that%20landmark%20step.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAmericans%20are%20also%20sickened%20by%20the%20never-ending%20rash%20of%20horrific%20school%20shootings%2C%20despite%20majority%20support%20for%20gun%20control.%20From%20the%20United%20Kingdom%20to%20Norway%2C%20gun-ownership%20laws%20are%20much%20stricter%20than%20in%20the%20United%20States%2C%20which%20is%20home%20to%20nearly%20half%20of%20the%20world's%20civilian-owned%20guns.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAll%20of%20which%20makes%20it%20no%20surprise%20that%20Democrats%20are%20far%20more%20likely%20to%20flee%20America%20than%20Republicans.%20Since%202015%2C%20Democrats%20Abroad%2C%20the%20foreign-based%20arm%20of%20the%20Democratic%20National%20Committee%2C%20has%20nearly%20tripled%20its%20membership%2C%20which%20now%20numbers%20in%20the%20hundreds%20of%20thousands.%20%26quot%3BWhen%20we%20do%20voter%20registration%2C%20we%20register%20everybody%2C%26quot%3B%20Martha%20McDevitt-Pugh%2C%20the%20international%20chair%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eof%20Democrats%20Abroad%2C%20told%20me%20on%20a%20Zoom%20call%20from%20her%20base%20in%20the%20Netherlands.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20we%20come%20overwhelmingly%20across%20Democrats%20who%20want%20to%20vote.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHollywood%20is%20further%20stoking%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ea%20seductive%20image%20of%20expat%20life.%20Netflix's%20smash%20hit%20%26quot%3BEmily%20in%20Paris%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20an%20inspiration%20for%20a%20new%20generation%20of%20American%20Francophiles%2C%20heirs%20to%20the%20likes%20of%20Ernest%20Hemingway%20and%20James%20Baldwin%20%E2%80%94%20is%20now%20shooting%20its%20fourth%20season.%20Leggett%20International%2C%20a%20real-estate%20agency%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ebased%20in%20France%2C%20hosts%20webinars%20targeting%20prospective%20US%20buyers%2C%20who%20comprise%20the%20largest%20share%20of%20its%20foreign%20clientele.%20In%20%26quot%3BExpats%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20new%20Amazon%20Prime%20series%20set%20in%20Hong%20Kong%2C%20Nicole%20Kidman's%20character%2C%20in%20the%20throes%20of%20a%20bedroom%20frolic%20with%20her%20husband%2C%20asks%3A%20%26quot%3BDon't%20you%20ever%20miss%20it%2C%20home%3F%26quot%3B%20He%20energetically%20replies%3A%20%26quot%3BI%20like%20my%20life%20here.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThen%20there's%20the%20growing%20trend%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eof%20%26quot%3Bdigital%20nomads%2C%26quot%3B%20who%20reject%20the%20antiquated%20concept%20of%20a%20fixed%20office%20in%20a%20post-COVID%20world.%20By%20one%20estimate%2C%20there%20are%20already%20some%2017%20million%20Americans%20roaming%20the%20globe%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0nearly%20half%20of%20all%20digital%20nomads%20worldwide.%20In%20the%20age%20of%20remote%20work%2C%20young%20people%20without%20enough%20savings%20or%20the%20credit%20to%20purchase%20foreign%20property%20suddenly%20find%20themselves%20able%20to%20pack%20up%20and%20leave%20America.%20And%20those%20who%20may%20depart%20in%20the%20wake%20of%20a%20second%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-met-with-elon-musk-for-potential-campaign-donation-nyt-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETrump%3C%2Fa%3E%20presidency%20can%20enjoy%20another%20benefit%20of%20life%20abroad.%20The%20website%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2FNomadList.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENomadList.com%3C%2Fa%3E%20helpfully%20informs%20remote%20workers%20that%20there%20are%20now%20429%20cities%20where%20marijuana%20is%20legal%2C%20from%20Bangkok%20to%20Buenos%20Aires.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20fairness%2C%20those%20who%20flee%20America%20to%20escape%20MAGA%20may%20find%20themselves%20confronted%20by%20a%20host%20of%20unpleasant%20surprises.%20The%20headaches%20start%20with%20the%20red%20tape.%20On%20any%20given%20day%2C%20my%20Expats%20in%20Italy%20Facebook%20group%20teems%20with%20the%20sort%20of%20questions%20that%20can%20drive%20a%20novice%20foreign-property%20owner%20batty.%20Why%20won't%20my%20Italian%20utility%20company%20let%20me%20pay%20my%20bill%20with%20a%20US%20credit%20card%3F%20(Answer%3A%20Because%20it%20won't.)%20Property%20bidders%20must%20have%20their%20offers%20officially%20registered%20with%20the%20local%20municipality%20and%20verified%20by%20the%20godlike%20person%20known%20as%20the%20%26quot%3Bnotaio%2C%26quot%3B%20an%20official%20of%20ancient%20standing%20who%20drafts%20and%20authenticates%20the%20raft%20of%20documents%20for%20a%20fair-size%20fee.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThen%20there%20are%20the%20tax-reporting%20requirements.%20In%202010%2C%20Congress%20enacted%20the%20Foreign%20Account%20Tax%20Compliance%20Act%2C%20which%20was%20designed%20to%20keep%20wealthy%20Americans%20with%20substantial%20foreign%20assets%20from%20evading%20their%20tax%20obligations.%2