%20took%20a%20ride%20in%20it%20while%20interacting%20with%20several%20schoolgoers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Prime%20Minister%20said%20modernising%20public%20transport%20is%20a%20priority%20for%20his%20government.%20Several%20generations%2C%20he%20said%2C%20have%20grown%20up%20looking%20at%20Kolkata%20Metro.%20%26quot%3BWhen%20I%20first%20came%20to%20Kolkata%20as%20a%20child%2C%20seeing%20the%20Metro%20was%20an%20attraction.%20But%20today%2C%20the%20Kolkata%20Metro%20is%20also%20a%20witness%20to%20the%20fast%20pace%20at%20which%20the%20BJP%20government%20works.%20In%20the%2040%20years%20before%202014%2C%20the%20Kolkata%20Metro%20route%20expanded%20to%2028%20km.%20But%20in%20the%20past%2010%20years%2C%2031%20km%20of%20Metro%20route%20have%20been%20added.%20The%20BJP%20government%20has%20worked%20very%20honestly%20for%20the%20development%20of%20Bengal%20and%20the%20country%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELeaders%20of%20the%20Opposition's%20INDIA%20alliance%2C%20of%20which%20the%20Mamata%20Banerjee-led%20Trinamool%20Congress%20is%20a%20part%2C%20are%20scared%20as%20the%20BJP%20is%20set%20to%20return%20to%20power%2C%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20said.%20%26quot%3BThey%20are%20losing%20their%20sleep%20and%20their%20balance%2C%20so%20they%20have%20started%20abusing%20Modi%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLeaders%20of%20the%20INDIA%20alliance%20are%20now%20saying%20that%20I%20talk%20against%20dynastic%20politics%20because%20I%20have%20no%20family.%20They%20want%20to%20know%20where%20my%20family%20is.%20These%20dynasts%20should%20come%20here.%20This%20is%20Modi%20ka%20parivar%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20doubling%20down%20on%20the%20BJP's%20campaign%20to%20counter%20RJD%20patriarch%20Lalu%20Yadav's%20%26quot%3BModi%20has%20no%20family%26quot%3B%20jab.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPointing%20at%20the%20women%20in%20the%20crowd%2C%20he%20said%20the%20mothers%2C%20sisters%20and%20daughters%20shield%20him%20from%20every%20difficulty.%20%26quot%3BFor%20me%2C%20the%20mothers%20and%20sisters%20of%20Bengal%20rise%20like%20Goddess%20Durga%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Prime%20Minister%20said%20he%20left%20home%20at%20a%20young%20age%20and%20wandered%20across%20the%20country.%20%26quot%3BI%20did%20not%20have%20a%20dime%20in%20my%20pocket.%20But%20you%20would%20be%20proud%20to%20know%20that%20one%20or%20the%20other%20family%20would%20ask%20me%20daily%20if%20I%20have%20eaten.%20I%20roamed%20around%20with%20a%20jhola%2C%20but%20I%20never%20spent%20a%20day%20hungry.%20That's%20why%20I%20say%20140%20crore%20people%20of%20this%20country%20are%20my%20family%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20adding%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20am%20now%20trying%20to%20repay%20those%20favours.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBengal's%20women%20power%2C%20he%20said%2C%20has%20given%20a%20direction%20to%20the%20country.%20%26quot%3BBut%2C%20in%20this%20land%2C%20under%20the%20Trinamool%20rule%2C%20women%20have%20suffered%20atrocities.%20Trinamool%20has%20committed%20a%20grave%20sin.%20What%20happened%20in%20Sandeshkhali%20would%20make%20everyone%20hang%20their%20heads%20in%20shame.%20But%20the%20Trinamool%20government%20doesn't%20care%20about%20your%20pain.%20It%20is%20using%20all%20its%20might%20to%20protect%20the%20oppressor%20of%20Bengali%20women%2C%20but%20they%20have%20faced%20jolts%20in%20the%20high%20court%20and%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20PM's%20barbs%20at%20the%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20government%20come%20against%20the%20backdrop%20of%20the%20tug%20of%20war%20between%20Bengal%20police%20and%20the%20CBI%20over%20Sheikh%20Shahjahan's%20custody.%20The%20Calcutta%20High%20Court%20has%20asked%20Bengal%20police%20to%20hand%20over%20Shahjahan%20to%20the%20central%20agency.%20The%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20government%20has%20challenged%20the%20ruling%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20and%20refused%20to%20hand%20him%20over%20till%20the%20court%20takes%20a%20decision.%20Shahjahan%20was%20earlier%20arrested%20after%20being%20on%20the%20run%20for%2052%20days.%20While%20the%20Trinamool%20has%20expelled%20him%2C%20the%20BJP%20says%20people%20of%20Sandeshkhali%2C%20who%20have%20accused%20him%20and%20his%20aides%20of%20sexual%20harassment%2C%20land%20grab%20and%20extortion%2C%20will%20get%20no%20justice%20till%20central%20agency%20grills%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Trinamool%20government%2C%20he%20said%2C%20trusts%20leaders%20who%20commit%20atrocities%2C%20but%20not%20the%20women%20of%20the%20state.%20%26quot%3BWomen%20from%20Bengal%20and%20the%20country%20are%20outraged.%20This%20storm%20won't%20remain%20restricted%20to%20Sandeshkhali.%20It%20will%20reach%20the%20whole%20Bengal.%20Bengal's%20Nari%20Shakti%20has%20set%20out%20to%20destroy%20Trinamool's%20Mafia%20rule.%20Sandeshkhali%20has%20shown%20that%20only%20BJP%20is%20the%20voice%20of%20the%20women%20of%20Bengal.%20The%20Trinamool%20government%2C%20under%20the%20pressure%20of%20appeasement%20and%20extortionists%2C%20will%20never%20help%20women%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECalling%20the%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20government%20%26quot%3Banti-women%26quot%3B%2C%20he%20said%20several%20welfare%20schemes%20launched%20for%20women%20have%20not%20been%20implemented%20in%20Bengal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Prime%20Minister%20also%20met%20a%20group%20of%20women%20from%20the%20Sandeshkhali%20island.%20%26quot%3BAfter%20the%20public%20meeting%2C%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20met%20a%20few%20women%20from%20Sandeshkhali.%20They%20narrated%20their%20ordeal%20and%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20heard%20them%20patiently%20like%20a%20father%20figure.%20The%20victims%20were%20very%20emotional%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20party%20source%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShortly%20after%20the%20Prime%20Minister's%20address%2C%20the%20Trinamool%20Congress%20hit%20back.%20Leading%20the%20charge%2C%20party%20MP%20Derek%20O'Brien%20said%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20has%20no%20right%20to%20lecture%20on%20women's%20security%20as%20a%20BJP%20