C%20and%20many%20true%20believers%20never%20sell%2C%20no%20matter%20what%20happens.%20And%20hey%2C%20maybe%20this%20will%20all%20work%20out%20this%20time%2C%20but%20it's%20impossible%20not%20to%20recognize%20the%20pattern%20here.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBitcoin%20from%20the%20earliest%20days%20has%20been%20very%20volatile%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20David%20Yermack%2C%20a%20professor%20of%20finance%20and%20business%20transformation%20at%20New%20York%20University's%20Stern%20School%20of%20Business.%20%26quot%3BWhat%20you're%20seeing%20now%20is%20entirely%20consistent%20with%20its%20history.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20main%20explanation%20for%20the%20recent%20gain%20in%20bitcoin's%20price%20is%20the%20Securities%20and%20Exchange%20Commission's%20begrudged%20blessing%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fcurrencies%2Fspot-bitcoin-etf-sec-approval-us-trading-btc-price-outlook-2024-1%3F_gl%3D1*1aj9dy2*_ga*MTI3NzY0MTgwNS4xNzA1OTU4MTA0*_ga_E21CV80ZCZ*MTcwOTU4NTk2OS4xNzIuMS4xNzA5NTg3MTM4LjU0LjAuMA..%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Espot%20bitcoin%20exchange-traded%20funds%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20investment%20vehicles%20that%20track%20bitcoin's%20price.%20They're%20more%20accessible%20for%20investors%2C%20easier%20to%20trade%2C%20and%20better%20regulated%20than%20a%20direct%20investment%20in%20bitcoin.%20Like%20all%20ETFs%2C%20they%20also%20come%20with%20a%20small%20fee.%20The%20SEC%20approved%20nearly%20a%20dozen%20of%20these%20funds%2C%20including%20products%20from%20Wall%20Street%20stalwarts%20such%20as%20Fidelity%20and%20BlackRock%2C%20who've%20come%20around%20on%20the%20asset%20class%20after%20years%20of%20saying%20bitcoin%20gave%20them%20the%20ick.%20This%20has%20helped%20legitimize%20the%20asset%20class%20and%20made%20more%20people%20comfortable%20investing%20in%20it%2C%20especially%20when%20it's%20packaged%20in%20the%20familiar%20ETF%20format.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20ETFs%20have%20gotten%20popular%20fast%3A%20The%2010%20leading%20bitcoin%20ETFs%20have%20taken%20in%20%247.3%20billion%20in%20inflows%20since%20their%20debut.%20Hundreds%20of%20millions%20of%20dollars%20poured%20in%20after%20the%20SEC's%20approval%20in%20January.%20BlackRock's%20iShares%20Bitcoin%20Trust%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bloomberg.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2F2024-03-03%2Fblackrock-and-fidelity-capitalize-on-fomo-from-spot-bitcoin-etf-mania%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eraked%20in%3C%2Fa%3E%20over%20%24500%20million%20a%20day%20in%20the%20final%20three%20days%20of%20February.%20This%20week%2C%20Fidelity%20saw%20%24400%20million%20in%20inflows%20in%20a%20single%20day.%20As%20bitcoin%20ETF%20providers%20have%20to%20invest%20in%20the%20underlying%20assets%20%E2%80%94%20bitcoins%20%E2%80%94%20demand%20for%20those%20assets%20increases.%20And%20as%20bullishness%20around%20the%20cryptocurrency%20picks%20up%2C%20investors%20start%20directly%20buying%20bitcoin%2C%20too.%20This%20creates%20a%20virtuous%20cycle%20of%20demand%20and%20boosts%20the%20price.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEric%20Balchunas%2C%20a%20senior%20ETF%20analyst%20at%20Bloomberg%20Intelligence%2C%20described%20the%20degree%20to%20which%20the%20bitcoin%20ETFs%20have%20taken%20off%20as%20%26quot%3Bpretty%20unprecedented.%26quot%3B%20He%20figured%20this%20would%20be%20more%20analogous%20to%20the%20launch%20in%202004%20of%20the%20first%20gold%20ETF%2C%20which%20cooled%20off%20quickly%20after%20a%20hot%20start.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20speed%20of%20the%20come-up%20is%20much%20faster%20than%20I%20thought%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20he%20was%20specifically%20surprised%20at%20retail-trader%20activity%20in%20the%20bitcoin%20ETFs.%20%26quot%3BI%20thought%20we'd%20see%20bigger%2C%20chunkier%20advisors%2C%20almost%20like%20medium-sized%20or%20big%20fish%20fighting.%20I%20underestimated%20the%20amount%20of%20minnows.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPeople%20I%20spoke%20with%20about%20bitcoin's%20current%20run%20had%20a%20range%20of%20theories%20about%20its%20factors%20aside%20from%20the%20ETF%20go-ahead.%20James%20Butterfill%2C%20the%20head%20of%20research%20at%20CoinShares%2C%20told%20me%20this%20rally%20is%20more%20%26quot%3Bfundamentals%20driven%26quot%3B%20than%20rallies%20in%20years%20past.%20The%20prospect%20of%20interest-rate%20cuts%20by%20the%20Federal%20Reserve%20has%20investors%20of%20all%20stripes%20bullish%20on%20riskier%20assets%2C%20including%20crypto.%20In%20April%2C%20a%20so-called%20halving%2C%20which%20happens%20every%20four%20years%2C%20will%20cut%20the%20rate%20at%20which%20miners%20can%20create%20new%20bitcoins%3B%20the%20idea%20is%20that%20by%20slowing%20the%20supply%20of%20new%20bitcoins%2C%20the%20price%20will%20increase%2C%20though%20it's%20not%20clear%20how%20much%20of%20an%20effect%20it%20has%20since%20everyone%20knows%20it's%20coming.%20(Also%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fcurrencies%2Fbitcoin-price-outlook-risks-cryptocurrency-drop-spot-etf-halving-april-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Enot%20everyone%20agrees%3C%2Fa%3E%20it%20will%20be%20good%20for%20bitcoin's%20price.)%20Others%20pointed%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcointelegraph.com%2Flearn%2Fwhat-is-the-lightning-network-in-bitcoin-and-how-does-it-work%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etechnological%20improvements%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20crypto%20and%20bitcoin%2C%20or%20to%20troubles%20at%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnew-york-community-bank-nycb-shares-turmoil-ceo-internal-controls-crisis-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENew%20York%20Community%20Bancorp%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20or%20to%20Argentina's%20presidential%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20then%20there's%20just%20good%20old%20speculation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20still%20think%20that's%20an%20element%20pushing%20up%20prices%20this%20time%2C%20too%2C%26quot%3B%20Butterfill%20said%2C%20%26quot%3Band%20maybe%20a%20little%20bit%20of%20FOMO%2C%20as%20people%20like%20to%20put%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOf%20course%2C%20whenever%20there's%20a%20sudden%20boom%20in%20bitcoin%2C%20the%20next%20question%20is%20when%20is%20the%20bust%20coming%3F%20It's%20impossible%20to%20predict%20the%20future%2C%20but%20past%20bitcoin%20crashes%20have%20been%20precipitated%20by%20different%20events%3A%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.latimes.com%2Fbusiness%2Fhiltzik%2Fla-fi-mh-the-bitcoin-crash-20131207-story.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eregulatory%20crackdowns%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20exchange%20breaches%2C%20product%20collapses%2C%20bubbles%20just%20bursting.%20Perhaps%20the%20very%20thing%20driving%20the%20rally%2C%20the%20ETFs%2C%20could%20be%20the%20boom's%20undoing%20%E2%80%94%20investors%20start%20pulling%20out%2C%20so%20the%20funds%20start%20selling%20the%20underlying%20assets%2C%20and%20the%20upward%20spiral%20becomes%20a%20downward%20one.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPlenty%20of%20other%20cryptocurrencies%20have%20surged%3A%20ether%2C%20litecoin%2C%20dogecoin%2C%20shiba%20inu%20coin%2C%20insert-meme-here%20coin.%20And%20except%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2F5-proposed-ethereum-etfs-to-keep-your-eyes-on-1033081043%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eether%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20they%20don't%20appear%20to%20have%20an%20ETF%20(or%20purpose)%20on%20the%20horizon.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20the%20kind%20of%20really%20nihilistic%20speculative%20activity%20that%20characterized%20the%20end%20of%20the%20previous%20bull%20markets%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Nic%20Carter%2C%20a%20general%20partner%20at%20Castle%20Island%20Ventures%2C%20adding%20that%20this%20crypto%20activity%20isn't%20necessarily%20cause%20for%20optimism%20about%20bitcoin's%20future.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOr%20maybe%2C%20just%20maybe%2C%20the%20latest%20run%20will%20cement%20bitcoin's%20future%20as%20a%20more%20stable%20part%20of%20people's%20investment%20portfolios.%20Carter%20told%20me%20that%20while%20there's%20a%20lot%20of%20excitement%20at%20the%20moment%2C%20he%20thinks%20bitcoin%20is%20on%20its%20way%20to%20being%20a%20%26quot%3Bboring%26quot%3B%20asset%20as%20it%20becomes%20more%20institutional%20and%20as%20the%20ETFs%20provide%20more-permanent%20buy%20pressure.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere's%20not%20a%20lot%20of%20uncertainty%20left%20about%20bitcoin.%20It%20became%20a%20key%20financial%20asset.%20It%20achieved%20its%20destiny%2C%20and%20now%20that%20it's%20there%2C%20I%20think%20there'll%20be%20slower%20growth%20but%20also%20less%20downside%20volatility%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20though%20he%20didn't%20rule%20out%20some%20potential%20for%20mania.%20Bitcoin%20dipping%20by%20nearly%2010%25%20hours%20after%20hitting%20an%20all-time%20high%20would%20suggest%20mania%20is%20still%20in%20the%20equation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20overarching%20theme%20of%20bitcoin%20remains%20what%20it's%20always%20been%3A%20It's%20volatile%2C%20and%20with%20that%20volatility%20comes%20risk.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBitcoin%20has%20always%20exhibited%20a%20fair%20amount%20of%20what%20we%20call%20momentum%20trading%2C%20which%20is%20that%20once%20it%20starts%20to%20move%2C%20people%20jump%20on%20the%20train%20for%20fear%20of%20missing%20out%2C%26quot%3B%20Yermack%20said.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20this%20works%20in%20two%20directions.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20ride%20up%20has%20some%20familiar%20elements.%20The%20bitcoiners%20claim%20victory%2C%20the%20naysayers%20wag%20their%20fingers%2C%20and%20at%20some%20point%20a%20friend%20from%20high%20school%20texts%20to%20ask%20if%20crypto%20is%20a%20good%20way%20to%20make%20quick%20money%20%E2%80%94%20a%20sign%20the%20peak%20is%20near.%20The%20ride%20down%20looks%20similar%2C%20too.%20The%20people%20who%20didn't%20buy%20in%20laugh%20at%20the%20ones%20who%20did%2C%20and%20a%20cast%20of%20characters%20come%20out%20to%20declare%20the%20crypto%20endeavor%20is%20dead.%20Rinse%20and%20repeat.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInvestors%20are%20back%20on%20the%20bitcoin%20roller%20coaster%20%E2%80%94%20and%20it%20