%20the%20Imagi%20Meira%20civil%20society%20group.%20Their%20demand%20has%20been%20to%20place%20in%20the%20House%20a%20report%20by%20the%20Privilege%20Ethics%20Committee%20against%20the%2010%20Kuki%20legislators%20for%20%E2%80%9Ctrying%20to%20disintegrate%20Manipur%E2%80%9D%20in%20spite%20of%20taking%20an%20oath%20in%20the%20assembly%20to%20protect%20the%20state%20and%20serve%20its%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EImagi%20Meira%20convenor%20Thounoujam%20Sujata%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ifp.co.in%2Fmanipur%2Fmanipur-police-foils-attempt-to-storm-assembly%5C%22%3Etold%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20%3Cem%3EImphal%20Free%20Press%3C%2Fem%3E%20on%20March%204%20that%20the%20women%E2%80%99s%20body%20has%20been%20demanding%20a%20report%20on%20the%20matter%20from%20the%20Committee%2C%20and%20had%20decided%20to%20march%20towards%20it%20since%20it%20was%20not%20done%20even%20on%20the%20last%20day%20of%20the%20session.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EThe%20report%20quoting%20Th.%20Sujata%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20issue%20needs%20to%20be%20discussed%20on%20the%20assembly%20floor%20as%20what%20action%20should%20be%20taken%20against%20those%2010%20MLAs%20trying%20to%20disintegrate%20Manipur.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EQuestioning%20the%20N.%20Biren%20Singh%20government%20about%20not%20taking%20any%20action%20against%20those%20elected%20leaders%2C%20Sujata%20told%20the%20Imphal-based%20daily%20that%20the%20chief%20minister%20had%20%E2%80%9Calso%20expressed%20earlier%20that%20the%20present%20crisis%20is%20instigated%20by%20the%20Kuki%20narco-terrorists.%20Therefore%2C%20demanding%20a%20separate%20administration%20by%20the%2010%20Kuki-Zo%20MLAs%20showed%20that%20they%20are%20also%20supporting%20the%20narco-terrorists.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EThis%20is%20the%20second%20time%20since%20the%20ethnic%20strife%20broke%20out%20between%20the%20Meiteis%20and%20the%20Kukis%20that%20the%2060-member%20state%20assembly%20had%20met.%20On%20both%20counts%2C%20the%2010%20Kuki%20MLAs%20and%20the%20majority%20of%20the%2010%20Naga%20MLAs%20had%20stayed%20away%20from%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EBefore%20the%20House%20adjourned%20after%20a%20five-day%20session%2C%20chief%20minister%20Singh%20told%20the%20legislators%20that%20two%20meetings%20of%20the%20tribal%20legislators%20have%20so%20far%20been%20conducted%20at%20the%20behest%20of%20the%20Union%20government%20%E2%80%93%20one%20in%20New%20Delhi%20and%20one%20recently%20in%20Guwahati%20%E2%80%93%20to%20break%20the%20deadlock%20between%20the%20two%20communities%2C%20including%20an%20attempt%20to%20bring%20them%20back%20to%20the%20House.%20He%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CA%20third%20meeting%20will%20be%20held%20with%20the%20chairman%20of%20the%20hill%20area%20committee%20(HAC).%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3ETwo%20days%20ago%2C%20the%20chief%20minister%20had%20disclosed%20to%20the%20House%20that%20a%20%E2%80%9C%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ifp.co.in%2Fmanipur%2Fmanipur-crisis-reconciliation-team-set-up%5C%22%3Ereconciliation%20team%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%9D%20under%20the%20leadership%20of%20HAC%20chairman%20Dinganglung%20Gangmei%20had%20been%20formed%3B%20Gangmei%20was%20among%20several%20leaders%20to%20have%20met%20the%20aggrieved%20Kuki%20legislators%20in%20Guwahati%20this%20past%20February.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EThe%20chief%20minister%E2%80%99s%20March%204%20statement%20was%20in%20response%20to%20the%20former%20chief%20minister%20and%20Congress%20veteran%20Okram%20Ibobi%20Singh%E2%80%99s%20question%20to%20the%20government%20as%20to%20why%20the%20Union%20government%20had%20stayed%20away%20from%20directly%20dealing%20with%20the%20Manipur%20crisis.%20Ibobi%20Singh%20said%20it%20looked%20as%20if%20the%20Centre%20had%20left%20the%20people%20of%20Manipur%20to%20fight%20amongst%20themselves.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3ESingh%20had%20also%20suggested%20a%20third-party%20intervention%20to%20sort%20out%20the%20differences%20between%20the%20two%20communities%20and%20make%20arrangements%20to%20disarm%20people%20in%20the%20state%20so%20that%20incidents%20of%20violence%20and%20the%20atmosphere%20of%20fear%20could%20be%20tamed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EIn%20reply%2C%20the%20chief%20minister%20made%20a%20few%20startling%20statements%2C%20including%20that%20disarmament%20of%20the%20mob%20has%20%E2%80%9Can%20issue%20as%20one%20side%20took%20up%20arms%20due%20to%20being%20aggrieved%20(referring%20to%20Meitei%20groups%20like%20the%20Arambai%20Tenggol)%20while%20another%20side%20is%20the%20SoO%20militants%20(referring%20to%20the%20Kuki%20armed%20groups%20in%20peace%20talks%20with%20the%20Centre).%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EOn%20advised%20to%20meet%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20on%20the%20Manipur%20issue%20by%20the%20Opposition%20leader%2C%20the%20chief%20minister%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ifp.co.in%2Fmanipur%2Fibobi-moots-third-party-intervention-to-solve-manipur-crisis%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CHe%20was%20informed%20by%20(Union%20home%20minister)%20Amit%20Shah%20that%20the%20PM%20entrusted%20him%20to%20deal%20with%20the%20Manipur%20situation.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EThe%20chief%20minister%20also%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thesangaiexpress.com%2FEncyc%2F2024%2F3%2F6%2FBy-Our-Staff-ReporterIMPHAL-Mar-5-Even-though-the-Ministry-of-Home-Affairs-has-written-to-the-Ministry-of.html%5C%22%3Egave%20out%20some%20data%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20the%20missing%20persons%20cases%20during%20the%20ten-month-long%20violence%20in%20the%20north-eastern%20state.%20He%20said%20there%20were%2063%20missing%20cases%20in%20the%20course%20of%20the%20conflict%2C%20out%20of%20which%2026%20were%20found%20dead%2C%20nine%20found%20alive%20%E2%80%9Cbut%20the%20other%2028%20cannot%20be%20traced%20till%20date.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709719158000%2C