%20action%2C%20but%20he%20stands%20by%20his%20remarks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EP%20Wilson%2C%20DMK%20MP%20and%20counsel%20for%20Udhayanidhi%20Stalin%2C%20told%20NDTV%2C%20%26quot%3BIt%20is%20a%20big%20victory.%20The%20BJP%20distorted%20the%20speech.%20It%20was%20not%20against%20Hindu%20religion%20but%20only%20against%20caste%20discrimination%20and%20caste%20hegemony%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20row%20over%20his%20statement%20prompted%20police%20cases%20in%20several%20states%20of%20the%20country.%20The%20DMK%20leader%20has%20now%20approached%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20with%20the%20request%20that%20the%20multiple%20FIRs%20be%20clubbed%20into%20one.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20top%20court%20has%20responded%20sternly.%20A%20bench%20of%20Justice%20Sanjiv%20Khanna%20and%20Justice%20Dipankar%20Datta%20pulled%20him%20up%2C%20saying%20that%20as%20a%20minister%2C%20he%20should%20be%20aware%20of%20the%20consequences%20of%20his%20words.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20abuse%20your%20right%20under%20Article%2019(1)(a)%20(of%20the%20Constitution).%20You%20abuse%20your%20right%20under%20Article%2025.%20Now%20you%20are%20exercising%20your%20right%20under%20Article%2032%20(to%20file%20plea%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court)%3F%20Do%20you%20not%20know%20the%20consequences%20of%20what%20you%20said%3F%20You%20are%20not%20a%20layman.%20You%20are%20a%20minister.%20You%20should%20know%20the%20consequences%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20said%20Monday.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709718960000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2Fbnti32n4_udhayanidhi-stalin_625x300_02_February_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcourt-dismisses-petition-against-stalin-junior-over-sanatana-remarks-5186667%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Days%20after%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20pulled%20him%20for%20his%20remarks%20on%20Sanatana%20Dharma%2C%20DMK%20minister%20Udhayanidhi%20Stalin%20today%20got%20some%20relief%20from%20Madras%20High