wedding-of-anant-ambani-radhika-merchant%2Farticleshow%2F107896416.cms%3Ffrom%3Dmdr%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%20%E2%80%98Jammin%E2%80%99%20in%20Jamnagar%E2%80%99%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Feconomictimes.indiatimes.com%2Fnews%2Findia%2Fjammin-in-jamnagar-business-tech-elite-to-descend-for-wedding-of-anant-ambani-radhika-merchant%2Farticleshow%2F107896416.cms%3Ffrom%3Dmdr%5C%22%3E%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Economic%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Etermed%20it%2C%20was%20surely%20just%20a%20drop%20in%20Mukesh%20bhai%E2%80%99s%20ocean%20of%20wealth.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22281%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F04%2F04192003%2Fstatecraft.png%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-237577%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22233%5C%22%3ESo%2C%20never%20mind%20all%20that%20sniping%20from%20the%20sociologists%20who%20disapprove%20of%20conspicuous%20consumption%20or%20all%20those%20cussed%20moralists%20who%20would%20deride%20the%20Jamnagar%20extravaganza%20as%20a%20%E2%80%9Cvulgar%20display%20of%20wealth%3B%E2%80%9D%20nor%2C%20should%20you%2C%20Nita%20Ben%2C%20worry%20about%20the%20old%20elites%20of%20Old%20Bombay%20who%20can%20carry%20on%20sitting%20at%20home%20with%20their%20disapproving%20frowns%20and%2019%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Eth%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20century%20Victorian%20furniture.%20Like%20a%20true%20icon%2C%20you%20have%20created%20your%20own%20etiquette%20of%20taste%20and%20refinement.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAnd%2C%20thank%20you%2C%20so%20very%20much%20for%20those%20two%20minutes%20of%20extremely%20graceful%20Bharatnatyam%20on%20the%20third%20day%3B%20how%20can%20anyone%20be%20critical%20of%20someone%20at%20your%20age%20undertaking%20such%20a%20very%2C%20very%20personal%20yet%20very%20public%20ode%20to%20the%20new-couple-to-be.%20These%20two%20minutes%20were%C2%A0%20the%20cherry%20on%20the%20cake.%20In%20any%20case%2C%20you%20can%20tell%20off%20all%20the%20carping%20critics%20that%20you%20were%20rather%20mindful%20of%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20call%20to%20shun%20overseas%20%E2%80%9Cdestinations%20weddings.%E2%80%9D%20Without%20doubt%2C%20the%20same%20event%20and%20the%20same%20guests%20could%20have%20been%20summoned%20to%20any%20part%20of%20the%20world%3B%20instead%2C%20you%20chose%20to%20go%20back%20to%20your%20roots%2C%20to%20Bharat.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20all%20counts%2C%20you%20have%20no%20reason%20to%20be%20apologetic%20to%20anyone%3B%20rather%2C%20you%20deserve%20be%20congratulated%20not%20only%20for%20staging%20the%20pre-wedding%20event%20on%20such%20a%20grand%20scale%20but%20also%20for%20ensuring%2C%20through%20the%20Ambani%20group%E2%80%99s%20impressively%20competent%20public%20relationship%20machine%2C%20that%20the%20Indian%20masses%20were%20served%20up%20a%20daily%20slice%20of%20what%20was%20happening%20inside%20that%20highly%20secure%20zone%20in%20Jamnagar.%20As%20in%20the%20old%20feudal%20days%2C%20the%20populace%20felt%20it%20was%20entitled%20to%20vicariously%20enjoy%20the%20razzmatazz%20in%20royal%20households.%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIndeed%2C%20you%20and%20Mukesh%20Bhai%20need%20to%20be%20complimented%20for%20your%20perspicacity%20and%20sensitivity%20in%20realising%20that%20the%20%3Cem%3Ejanata%3C%2Fem%3E%20needed%20to%20be%20distracted%20from%20the%20misery%20and%20wretchedness%20of%20everyday%20life%20in%20New%20India.%20True%2C%20your%20countrymen%20could%20only%20gawk%20from%20a%20distance%20at%20all%20those%20glamorous%20celebrities%20as%20they%20danced%20and%20performed%20for%20you%20and%20your%20global%20guests%20but%20we%20needed%20some%20relief%20from%20the%20dollops%20of%20malice%20and%20below-the-belt-meanness%20that%20is%20dished%20out%20by%20Narendra%20Modi%20three%20times%20a%20week.%20As%20a%20nation%20and%20society%20we%20have%20not%20been%20permitted%20to%20relax%20or%C2%A0%20have%20a%20good%20time%3B%20your%20three-days%20of%20Jamnagar%20fun%20and%20frolic%20were%20much-needed%20comfort%3B%20for%20weeks%20we%20will%20keep%20ourselves%20busy%20over%20Kareena%20Kapoor%E2%80%99s%20necklace%20and%20how%20much%20the%20three%20Khans%20charged%20for%20shaking%20their%20legs.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBeyond%20this%20titillation%2C%20you%20have%20helped%20the%20middle%20classes%20absorb%20a%20few%20lessons.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFirst%2C%20we%20should%20all%20be%20so%20ever%20grateful%20to%20you%20for%20demonstrating%20that%20someone%20is%20higher%20than%20the%20Indian%20state.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWe%20have%20all%20thought%20that%20under%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi%2C%20the%20Indian%20state%20had%20become%20all%20too%20omnipotent%20and%20omnipresent%20as%20it%20has%20performed%20an%20unending%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Epranprathista%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20at%20the%20Church%20of%20National%20Security.%20The%20archbishops%20of%20this%20church%20have%20claimed%20for%20themselves%20the%20right%20to%20make%20more%20intrusive%20and%20more%20absolutist%20demands%20over%20our%20lives%20and%20liberties%3B%20but%2C%20the%20ease%20with%20which%20Jamnagar%20airport%20was%20re-designated%20to%20accommodate%20your%20guests%20from%20all%20around%20the%20world%20proves%20that%20concepts%C2%A0%20like%20%E2%80%9Cnational%20security%E2%80%9D%20and%20%E2%80%9Cnational%20defence%E2%80%9D%20are%20really%20flexible%20constructs.%20Next%20time%20when%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fa-timeline-of-umar-khalids-bail-hearings%5C%22%3EUmar%20Khalid%E2%80%99s%20bail%20application%20comes%20up%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20their%20Lordships%20would%20do%20well%20to%20apply%20the%20Jamnagar%20rules.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESecond%2C%20bringing%20Rihanna%20was%20a%20nice%20touch.%20