0in%20Gaza.%20WHO%20has%20reported%20that%20children%20are%20dying%20of%20starvation%20in%20two%20northern%20Gaza%20hospitals.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20World%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fmiddle-east%2Fisrael-hamas-war-joe-biden-urges-hamas-to-accept-gaza-ceasefire-deal-by-ramzan%2Farticleshow%2F108255104.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia-indiatimes-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fmiddle-east%2Fisrael-hamas-war-joe-biden-urges-hamas-to-accept-gaza-ceasefire-deal-by-ramzan%2Famp_articleshow%2F108255104.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fmiddle-east%2Fisrael-hamas-war-joe-biden-urges-hamas-to-accept-gaza-ceasefire-deal-by-ramzan%2Famp_articleshow%2F108255104.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22The%20Wire's%20Zeeshan%20Kaskar%2C%20Activist%20Shaila%20Yadav%20Honoured%20with%20Comrade%20Ashok%20Manohar%20Yuva%20Urja%20Award%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F06122628%2FUntitled-design-32.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPune%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Zeeshan%20Kaskar%20from%3Cem%3E%20The%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20Shaila%20Yadav%20from%20Aundh%2C%20Satara%2C%20have%20been%20honoured%20with%20the%20prestigious%20Comrade%20Ashok%20Manohar%20Yuva%20Urja%20Award%20for%20their%20%E2%80%9Csignificant%20contributions%20to%20society.%E2%80%9D%20Instituted%20in%202012%2C%20this%20award%20was%20introduced%20by%20the%20late%20activist%20and%20rationalist%20Govind%20Pansare.%20It%20celebrates%20the%20dedication%20of%20young%20activists%20in%20advocating%20for%20justice%20and%20empowerment%20in%20marginalised%20communities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShaila%20Yadav%E2%80%99s%20advocacy%20has%20been%20instrumental%20in%20raising%20awareness%20about%20governmental%20schemes%20and%20socio-political%20rights%20for%20Nomadic%20Tribes%20across%20Maharashtra.%20Zeeshan%20Kaskar%E2%80%99s%20video%20journalism%20on%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20has%20shed%20light%20on%20the%20dangers%20of%20religious%20intolerance%20and%20Hindutva%20politics%2C%20notably%20through%20his%20acclaimed%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dent9-lRFFsw%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Naf%20Rath%E2%80%99%20video%20series%3C%2Fa%3E.%20His%20poignant%20storytelling%2C%20depicting%20the%20struggles%20of%20marginalised%20groups%2C%20resonated%20deeply%20with%20the%20Comrade%20Ashok%20Manohar%20Yuva%20Urja%20Award%20jury%2C%20leading%20to%20his%20selection%20for%20this%20prestigious%20honour.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EComrade%20Ashok%20Manohar%20was%20a%20dedicated%20activist%20known%20for%20his%20staunch%20advocacy%20for%20social%20justice%20and%20his%20unwavering%20commitment%20to%20the%20rights%20of%20marginalised%20groups%20in%20Maharashtra.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20award%20ceremony%2C%20held%20at%20the%20Shivajinagar%20Shramik%20Bhavan%20on%20March%202%2C%20Saturday%20evening%2C%20witnessed%20the%20felicitation%20of%20Zeeshan%20and%20Shaila%20by%20veteran%20journalist%20Raju%20Parulekar.%20In%20her%20address%2C%20Shaila%20Yadav%20shared%20her%20inspiring%20journey%20from%20Aundh%2C%20reflecting%20on%20her%20resilience%20in%20overcoming%20obstacles%20to%20pursue%20education%20and%20advocate%20for%20the%20rights%20of%20displaced%20indigenous%20communities.%20Zeeshan%20Kaskar%2C%20in%20his%20speech%2C%20highlighted%20the%20growing%20spectre%20of%20communalism%20and%20divisions%20in%20India%2C%20drawing%20from%20his%20experiences%20while%20covering%20sensitive%20issues.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20event%20was%20presided%20by%20Dr.%20Anjali%20Sathe%2C%20President%20of%20Comrade%20Ashok%20Manohar%20Yuva%20Urja%20Award.%20In%20her%20statement%2C%20Dr%20Sathe%20said%20that%20Zeeshan%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%9Ccourage%20to%20confront%20the%20venomous%20tendencies%20of%20religious%20fanaticism%20through%20impactful%20video%20journalism%20deserves%20commendation.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20went%20on%20to%20say%20that%20the%20goal%20of%20this%20award%20is%20to%20recognise%20and%20honour%20the%20efforts%20of%20young%20activists%20who%20are%20working%20tirelessly%20to%20counteract%20the%20divisive%20forces%20of%20religious%20hatred.%20Through%20this%20recognition%2C%20we%20aim%20to%20inspire%20and%20encourage%20other%20young%20activists%20to%20follow%20in%20their%20footsteps%20and%20continue%20their%20noble%20endeavours%20in%20promoting%20unity%2C%20understanding%2C%20and%20social%20justice%20within%20our%20communities.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709708919000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F06122628%2FUntitled-design-32.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fmedia%2Fthe-wires-zeeshan-kaskar-activist-shaila-yadav-honoured-with-comrade-ashok-manohar-yuva-urja-award%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20award%20was%20instituted%20by%20rationalist%20and%20activist%20Govind%20Pansare%20in%202012%2C%20to%20honour%20and%20encourage%20those%20who%20work%20to%20push%20back%20religious%20hatred%20and%20divisive%20forces%20in%20society.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A16%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fmedia%2Fthe-wires-zeeshan-kaskar-activist-shaila-yadav-honoured-with-comrade-ashok-manohar-yuva-urja-award%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22School%20Students%20in%20Rajasthan%20Show%20It%20Is%20Easy%20to%20Be%20a%20Hindu%20Standing%20up%20For%20Muslims%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F06123115%2FUntitled-design-9.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3ECan%20the%20Muslims%20of%20India%20only%20hope%20to%20have%20normal%20days%20when%20the%20Hindus%20around%20them%20stand%20up%20to%20Hindutva%20excesses%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20question%20struck%20me%20after%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Findia%2Fa-school-play-a-clerical-mistake-and-an-interfaith-elopement-behind-the-suspension-of-3-muslim-teachers-over-conversion-claims-in-rajasthan-9189076%2F%5C%22%3EI%20read%20about%20the%20demonstration%20and%20agitation%20by%20Hindu%20students%20of%20a%20higher%20secondary%20school%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20Khajuri%20village%20in%20Rajasthan%E2%80%99s%20Kota%2C%20protesting%20against%20the%20suspension%20of%20their%20Muslim%20teachers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThree%20Muslim%20teachers%20of%20the%20school%20were%20accused%20of%20making%20students%20offer%20namaz%20and%20putting%20pressure%20on%20them%20for%20religious%20conversion.%20In%20a%20memorandum%20given%20to%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20controversial%20education%20minister%20Madan%20Dilawar%2C%20the%20Sarva%20Hindu%20Samaj%20%E2%80%93%20a%20joint%20platform%20of%20Hindutva%20organisations%20%E2%80%93%20alleged%20that%20these%20teachers%20were%20engaged%20in%20%E2%80%98Islamic%20jihadi%20activities%E2%80%99%2C%20%E2%80%98religious%20conversion%E2%80%99%20and%20%E2%80%98%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Flies-insistence-and-disregard-for-evidence-the-journey-of-love-jihad-laws%5C%22%3Elove%20jihad%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%98.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20said%20that%20these%20teachers%20had%20conspired%20to%20convert%20a%20Hindu%20girl%20of%20the%20village%20and%20get%20her%20married%20to%20a%20Muslim%20boy.%20The%20girl%E2%80%99s%20family%2C%20along%20with%20this%20forum%2C%20had%20already%20issued%20threats%20to%20these%20teachers.%20The%20clinching%20basis%20for%20this%20allegation%20turned%20out%20to%20be%20the%20fact%20that%20%E2%80%98Islam%E2%80%99%20was%20written%20in%20the%20school%20register%20in%20the%20religion%20column%20next%20to%20the%20girl%E2%80%99s%20name.%20This%2C%20they%20alleged%2C%20proves%20that%20she%20was%20converted%20into%20Islam%20in%20the%20school.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20girl%20issued%20a%20statement%20saying%20that%20she%20was%20an%20adult%20and%20that%20she%20married%20a%20Muslim%20man%20of%20her%20own%20free%20will.%20She%20also%20said%20that%20she%20has%20not%20become%20a%20Muslim%20and%20continues%20to%20be%20a%20Hindu.%20But%20the%20allegation%20kept%20being%20repeated.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fin-rajasthans-kota-teachers-get-the-stick-as-education-minister-madan-dilawar-goes-on-a-suspension-spree%2Farticle67904405.ece%5C%22%3EMinister%20Dilawar%20then%20jumped%20in%20and%20made%20allegations%20against%20the%20Muslim%20teachers%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Soon%2C%20the%20teachers%20were%20suspended.%20A%20video%20statement%2C%20allegedly%20made%20by%20a%20school%20student%2C%20started%20circulating%20in%20which%20he%20said%20that%20these%20teachers%20forced%20him%20to%20offer%20namaz%20in%20the%20school%20and%20were%20engaged%20in%20religious%20conversion%20efforts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAll%20this%20does%20not%20surprise%20us%20and%20has%20become%20very%20normal%20in%20the%20India%20of%20our%20times.%20But%20what%20happened%20next%20was%20unexpected%20and%20unprecedented%20in%20many%20ways.%20The%20students%20of%20the%20school%20demonstrated%20in%20front%20of%20the%20authorities%20against%20the%20punishment%20given%20to%20their%20teachers.%20They%20said%20that%20the%20allegations%20levelled%20against%20their%20teachers%20were%20baseless%20and%20absurd.%20Even%20the%20boy%20who%20had%20said%20on%20camera%20that%20he%20was%20forced%20to%20offer%20namaz%20came%20forward%20and%20said%20that%20his%20statement%20was%20false%20and%20that%20he%20was%20forced%20to%20do%20make%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20principal%20and%20other%20teachers%20of%20the%20school%20have%20also%20supported%20their%20fellow%20teachers.%20They%20also%20called%20these%20allegations%20baseless.%20The%20young%20woman%20marriage%20had%20nothing%20to%20do%20with%20the%20school%20and%20these%20teachers%2C%20they%20said.%20Writing%20%E2%80%98Islam%E2%80%99%20against%20her%20name%20in%20the%20school%20register%20was%20a%20mistake.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20must%20note%20that%20the%20majority%20of%20students%20in%20the%20school%20are%20Hindus%20and%20the%20remaining%20teachers%20are%20all%20Hindus.%20This%20fact%20makes%20their%20stand%20very%20significant.%20That%20a%20Hindu%20should%20speak%20up%20for%20a%20Muslim%20is%20an%20exception%20and%20a%20surprise%20in%20today%E2%80%99s%20India.%20But%20the%20ordinary%20Hindu%20students%20and%20teachers%20of%20Khajuri%20showed%20that%20this%20is%20very%20easy%20to%20do.%20To%20do%20this%20all%20you%20need%20to%20have%20the%20sense%20of%20right%20and%20wrong.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20this%20is%20now%20an%20anomaly.%20Are%20there%20such%20Hindus%20still%20left%20in%20India%20who%20not%20only%20find%20injustice%20towards%20Muslims%20bad%20but%20are%20also%20ready%20to%20take%20the%20trouble%20of%20fighting%20against%20it%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20not%20easy%20to%20stand%20in%20front%20of%20the%20above-mentioned%20Sarva%20Hindu%20Samaj%2C%20the%20Bajrang%20Dal%2C%20the%20Vishwa%20Hindu%20Parishad%2C%20the%20Rashtriya%20Swayamsevak%20Sangh%20or%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20because%20there%20significant%20power%20in%20and%20behind%20them.%20Very%20often%20we%20have%20seen%20that%20the%20police%20and%20administration%20are%20also%20with%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20know%20that%20good%20people%20cannot%20always%20stand%20before%20goons.%20They%20may%20disagree%20with%20their%20injustice%2C%20it%20might%20pain%20them%2C%20but%20the%20cost%20of%20protesting%20against%20it%20is%20very%20high.%20That%20is%20why%2C%20after%20Muslim%20teachers%20were%20punished%2C%20what%20their%20students%20and%20colleagues%20did%20in%20their%20solidarity%20is%20a%20remarkable%20yet%20difficult%20thing%20to%20want%20to%20see%20repeated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20raises%20the%20question%20as%20to%20whether%2C%20in%20order%20for%20Muslims%20to%20live%20a%20normal%20life%2C%20their%20neighbours%20will%20have%20to%20be%20exceptionally%20righteous%20and%20courageous.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20few%20months%20ago%2C%20a%20Muslim%20teacher%20narrated%20to%20me%20the%20story%20of%20his%20search%20for%20a%20house%20in%20Delhi.%20He%20told%20me%20how%20difficult%20it%20was%20for%20him%20to%20get%20a%20house%20because%20he%20was%20a%20Muslim.%20The%20house%20where%20he%20lived%20earlier%20belonged%20to%20a%20Hindu.%20Pressure%20was%20put%20on%20his%20landlord%20to%20evict%20him%20from%20the%20house%20and%20he%20was%20threatened%20that%20if%20he%20did%20not%20do%20so%2C%20a%20police%20report%20would%20be%20filed%20against%20him%2C%20saying%20that%20he%20had%20given%20his%20house%20to%20a%20terrorist.%20But%20the%20Hindu%20landlord%20remained%20firm.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECan%20every%20Hindu%20landlord%20be%20like%20him%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20organisations%20are%20always%20looking%20for%20some%20pretext%20to%20make%20the%20life%20of%20Muslims%20difficult%20and%20some%20new%20method%20to%20harass%20them%2C%20then%20it%20will%20become%20more%20and%20more%20difficult%20for%20them%20to%20live%20their%20daily%20lives%20normally%20on%20their%20own.%20Muslims%20also%20know%20that%20they%20should%20not%20expect%20protection%20from%20the%20government%20bodies%20since%20such%20organisations%20are%20now%20part%20of%20the%20state%20structure.%20In%20many%20cases%20we%20have%20seen%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fmuslims-targeted-in-128-demolitions-617-people-affected-amnesty-reports-on-bulldozer-action%5C%22%3Estate%20agencies%20themselves%20turning%20into%20oppressors%20of%20Muslims.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJust%20after%20this%20incident%20in%20Khajuri%20village%2C%20an%20incident%20in%20Alwar%20in%20Rajasthan%20came%20to%20light.%20A%20girl%20alleged%20that%20two%20girls%20were%20pressurising%20her%20to%20convert%20to%20Islam%20and%20marry%20a%20Muslim.%20The%20police%20immediately%20arrested%20all%20three%20of%20them.%20The%20police%20officer%20said%20that%20it%20is%20a%20matter%20of%20investigation%20whether%20this%20allegation%20was%20made%20due%20to%20a%20personal%20rivalry%20but%20it%20is%20noteworthy%20that%20they%20felt%20it%20necessary%20to%20arrest%20the%20Muslim%20girls%20and%20boys%20even%20before%20the%20investigation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELike%20in%20Khajuri%2C%20Muslim%20teachers%20were%20suspended%20as%20soon%20as%20allegations%20were%20made.%20Will%20these%20three%20Muslims%20be%20able%20to%20get%20the%20support%20of%20Hindus%20in%20Alwar%20the%20way%20the%20Muslims%20got%20in%20Khajuri%3F%20We%20know%20the%20answer.%20But%20can%20this%20answer%20not%20be%20changed%3F%20The%20young%20students%20of%20Khajuri%20have%20demonstrated%20that%20it%20is%20possible.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EApoorvanand%20is%20an%20academic%20and%20an%20author.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709708642000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F06123115%2FUntitled-design-9.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fhindu-muslim-rajasthan-khajuri-school-students%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Are%20there%20such%20Hindus%20still%20left%20in%20India%20who%20not%20only%20find%20injustice%20towards%20Muslims%20bad%20but%20are%20also%20ready%20to%20take%20the%20trouble%20of%20fighting%20against%20it%3F%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fhindu-muslim-rajasthan-khajuri-school-students%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Viral%3A%20Bengaluru%20mall's%20premium%20parking%20%40Rs%201%2C000%2Fhour%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709708465000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-108257163%2Cimgsize-68466.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Fbengaluru%2Fviral-bengaluru-malls-premium-parking-rs-1000%2Fhour-netizens-say-this-isnt-an-airport%2Farticleshow%2F108257157.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20photo%20of%20a%20parking%20spot%20charging%20Rs%201%2C000%20per%20hour%20at%20Bengaluru's%20UB%20City%20Mall%20has%20sparked%20outrage%20on%20social%20media.%20Users%20expressed%20concern%20over%20the%20high%20cost%20of%20living%20in%20the%20Silicon%20Valley%20of%20India.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22HADI%20KHAN%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Fbengaluru%2Fviral-bengaluru-malls-premium-parking-rs-1000%2Fhour-netizens-say-this-isnt-an-airport%2Farticleshow%2F108257157.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Supreme%20Court's%20%26quot%3BWaste%20Bin%26quot%3B%20Rap%20Over%20Deforestation%20In%20Corbett%20Tiger%20Reserve%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EComing%20down%20heavily%20on%20the%20Uttarakhand%20government%20for%20the%20felling%20of%20trees%20and%20illegal%20construction%20in%20Jim%20Corbett%20National%20Park%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20today%20said%20public%20trust%20had%20been%20thrown%20into%20the%20waste%20bin.%C2%A0Pulling%20up%20former%20state%20minister%20Harak%20Singh%20Rawat%20and%20former%20divisional%20forest%20officer%20Kishan%20Chand%2C%20it%20asked%20the%20Centre%20to%20form%20a%20committee%20that%20will%20recommend%20steps%20to%20mitigate%20the%20damage%20and%20recover%20the%20cost%20from%20those%20responsible.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bench%20of%20Justice%20BR%20Gavai%2C%20Justice%20PK%20Mishra%20and%20Justice%20Sandeep%20Mehta%20was%20hearing%20a%20petition%20by%20environment%20activist%20and%20lawyer%20Gaurav%20Bansal.%20Mr%20Bansal%20had%20challenged%20the%20Uttarakhand%20government's%20proposal%20for%20a%20tiger%20safari%20and%20a%20zoo%20with%20caged%20animals%20inside%20the%20national%20park.%20The%20matter%20brought%20under%20the%20spotlight%20illegal%20construction%20and%20deforestation%20inside%20the%20national%20park.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bench%20started%20with%20a%20quote%20from%20the%20epic%20Mahabharata%2C%20which%20means%20that%20a%20forest%20protects%20the%20tiger%20and%20the%20tiger%20protects%20the%20forest.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20tiger%20safari%20in%20the%20core%20area%2C%20it%20said%2C%20will%20be%20contrary%20to%20the%20provisions%20of%20tiger%20conservation.%20The%20court%2C%20however%2C%20allowed%20safari%20tours%20in%20the%20buffer%20zone%20of%20the%20popular%20national%20park%2C%20citing%20the%20employment%20it%20may%20generate.%20The%20court%20noted%20that%20such%20safari%20tours%20should%20follow%20the%20necessary%20guidelines.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPulling%20up%20Mr%20Rawat%20and%20Mr%20Chand%2C%20the%20court%20said%20this%20is%20a%20case%20where%20bureaucrats%20and%20politicians%20threw%20public%20trust%20doctrine%20in%20the%20waste%20bin.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20have%2C%20in%20blatant%20disregard%20of%20the%20law%20and%20for%20commercial%20purposes%2C%20indulged%20in%20mass%20felling%20of%20trees%20to%20construct%20buildings%20on%20the%20pretext%20of%20promotion%20of%20tourism%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20bench%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20it%20was%20%26quot%3Bamazed%20at%20the%20audacity%26quot%3B%20in%20giving%20rules%20a%20go-by.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20many%20as%206%2C000%20trees%20were%20felled%20in%20the%20national%20park%2C%20visited%20by%20thousands%20every%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20said%20that%20while%20figures%20show%20substantial%20reduction%20in%20poaching%20of%20tigers%2C%20%26quot%3Bground%20realities%20cannot%20be%20denied%26quot%3B.%20The%20court%20appointed%20a%20three-member%20committee%20to%20provide%20suggestions%20for%20efficient%20management%20of%20tiger%20reserves%20in%20the%20country.%20It%20asked%20the%20panel%20to%20submit%20a%20report%20within%20three%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20noted%20that%20the%20Central%20Bureau%20of%20Investigation%20(CBI)%20is%20already%20probing%20the%20matter.%20%26quot%3BThe%20CBI%20probe%20will%20only%20lead%20to%20finding%20out%20who%20is%20responsible%20for%20this.%20We%20are%20of%20the%20view%20that%20the%20State%20cannot%20run%20away%20from%20the%20responsibility%20of%20restoring%20the%20status%20of%20the%20forest%20from%20when%20damage%20was%20done%20and%20recover%20it%20from%20the%20ones%20who%20committed%20the%20damage%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20court%20said%2C%20asking%20the%20central%20agency%20to%20file%20a%20status%20report%20in%20three%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709708100000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2Flf6403lo_jim-corbett-national-park_625x300_06_March_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsupreme-courts-waste-bin-rap-over-deforestation-in-corbett-tiger-reserve-5185757%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Coming%20down%20heavily%20on%20the%20Uttarakhand%20government%20for%20the%20felling%20of%20trees%20and%20illegal%20construction%20in%20Jim%20Corbett%20National%20Park%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20today%20said%20public%20trust%20had%20been%20thrown%20into%20the%20waste%20bin%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsupreme-courts-waste-bin-rap-over-deforestation-in-corbett-tiger-reserve-5185757%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsupreme-courts-waste-bin-rap-over-deforestation-in-corbett-tiger-reserve-5185757%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsupreme-courts-waste-bin-rap-over-deforestation-in-corbett-tiger-reserve-5185757%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Australian%20used%20cable%20ties%20to%20detain%20children%20-%20police%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709707754000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2FF284%2Fproduction%2F_132848026_240306cabletiedkidsstill2v2.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-australia-68487304%230%22%2C%