20Haley%20spokesperson%20Olivia%20Perez-Cubas%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%20%26quot%3BUnity%20is%20not%20achieved%20by%20simply%20claiming%20'we're%20united.'%26quot%3B%20Ms%20Haley's%20campaign%20said%20there%20remains%20a%20%26quot%3Blarge%20block%20of%20Republican%20primary%20voters%20who%20are%20expressing%20deep%20concerns%26quot%3B%20about%20the%20former%20president.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat%20is%20not%20the%20unity%20our%20party%20needs%20for%20success.%20Addressing%20those%20voters'%20concerns%20will%20make%20the%20Republican%20Party%20and%20America%20better%2C%26quot%3B%20Perez-Cubas%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Trump%20has%20a%20formidable%20delegate%20lead%20with%20893%20delegates%2C%20while%20Ms%20Haley%20has%2066.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20win%20the%20presidential%20nomination%20of%20the%20Republican%20party%2C%20either%20of%20the%20two%20candidates%20needs%201%2C215%20delegates.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPolitical%20pundits%20had%20pointed%20to%20Vermont%20as%20Ms%20Haley's%20best%20chance%20to%20win%20a%20state%2C%20especially%20given%20its%20history%20of%20favouring%20moderate%20Republican%20candidates.%20Adding%20to%20that%20advantage%2C%20she%20received%20a%20crucial%20endorsement%20from%20Vermont%20Governor%20Phil%20Scott%20over%20the%20weekend.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BVermont%20has%20a%20history%20of%20favouring%20moderate%20Republican%20candidates%2C%20and%20she%20got%20the%20endorsement%20of%20Governor%20Scott%20over%20the%20weekend.%20I%20don't%20think%20that%20makes%20her%20a%20favourite%2C%20but%20she%20has%20her%20best%20shot%2C%26quot%3B%20University%20of%20Vermont%20political%20science%20professor%20Alex%20Garlick%20told%20USA%20Today.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVermont's%20primary%20operates%20on%20a%20winner-takes-all%20basis%2C%20offering%2017%20delegates%20to%20the%20candidate%20who%20secures%2050%20per%20cent%20or%20more%20of%20the%20statewide%20vote.%20Otherwise%2C%20the%20delegates%20will%20be%20divided%20among%20Ms%20Haley%