%20questioned%20by%20officials.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20March%205%20%E2%80%93%20a%20day%20when%20the%20Bombay%20high%20court%20acquitted%20former%20Delhi%20University%20professor%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Fsearch%3Fq%3Dsaibaba%2Bthe%2Bwire%26oq%3Dsaibaba%2Bthe%2Bwire%26gs_lcrp%3DEgZjaHJvbWUyBggAEEUYOTIHCAEQIRigATIHCAIQIRigAdIBCDQ5MjFqMGo0qAIAsAIA%26sourceid%3Dchrome%26ie%3DUTF-8%5C%22%3EG.N%20Saibaba%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20others%20in%20a%20case%20linking%20them%20to%20Maoists%20%E2%80%93%20police%20in%20UP%20said%20they%20arrested%20Kripa%20Shanker%20Singh%2C%2049%2C%20and%20his%20wife%20Binda%20Sona%20alias%20Manju%2C%2041%2C%20from%20Prayagraj.%20Singh%20is%20a%20lawyer%20and%20practises%20in%20the%20high%20court%20while%20his%20wife%20used%20to%20teach%20at%20a%20private%20school%20but%20now%20works%20as%20a%20private%20typist%20in%20the%20high%20court%2C%20said%20an%20activist%20familiar%20with%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20was%20the%20second%20such%20event%20in%20less%20than%20five%20months%20when%20the%20Anti-Terrorist%20Squad%20of%20the%20police%20arrested%20an%20activist%20couple%20for%20alleged%20Naxal%20links%20merely%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20analysis%20of%20data%20extracted%20from%20their%20phones%20and%20laptops%20seized%20more%20than%20four%20years%20ago.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20as%20exclusively%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fanita-aazad-prabha-kushwaha-miscarriage-jail-medical-bail-maoist-link%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20in%20December%202023%2C%20a%2038-year-old%20activist%20Anita%20Aazad%20alias%20Prabha%20suffered%20a%20miscarriage%20in%20prison%20a%20week%20after%20a%20court%20in%20Lucknow%20dismissed%20her%20plea%20for%20bail%20on%20medical%20grounds%20of%20a%20high-risk%20pregnancy.%20Aazad%20and%20her%20husband%20and%20fellow%20activist%20Brijesh%20Kushwaha%20were%20arrested%20on%20October%2018%2C%202023%20more%20than%20four%20years%20after%20the%20UP%20ATS%20questioned%20them%20for%20suspected%20Naxal%20links%20and%20seized%20their%20devices.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fanita-aazad-prabha-kushwaha-miscarriage-jail-medical-bail-maoist-link%5C%22%3EWoman%20Jailed%20Over%20%E2%80%98Maoist%20Links%E2%80%99%20Miscarries%20a%20Week%20After%20Court%20Dismisses%20Medical%20Bail%20Plea%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERegarding%20the%20arrest%20of%20Kripa%20Shanker%20Singh%20and%20his%20wife%20Binda%20Sona%2C%20the%20ATS%20claimed%20that%20it%20had%20found%20%E2%80%9Cdocumented%20evidence%E2%80%9D%20on%20the%20examination%20of%20the%20FSL%20(Forensic%20Science%20Laboratory)%20report%20of%20the%20electronic%20devices%20including%20the%20laptop%20of%20the%20couple.%20The%20police%20also%20alleged%20that%20the%20material%20extracted%20from%20the%20couple%E2%80%99s%20devices%20proved%20that%20they%20were%20primary%20members%20of%20the%20banned%20outfit%20Communist%20Party%20of%20India%20(Maoist)%2C%20were%20involved%20in%20a%20%E2%80%9Cconspiracy%E2%80%9D%20to%20%E2%80%9Cwage%20war%20against%20India%E2%80%9D%20and%20for%20this%20purpose%20were%20trying%20to%20allure%20%E2%80%9Cfarmers%2C%20workers%20and%20the%20petty%20bourgeoisie%E2%80%9D%20to%20work%20for%20the%20outfit.%20The%20police%2C%20however%2C%20did%20not%20reveal%20the%20nature%20of%20the%20material%20extracted%20by%20them%20and%20how%20it%20incriminated%20the%20couple.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20couple%20was%20arrested%20in%20connection%20with%20an%20FIR%20lodged%20by%20the%20ATS%20in%202019.%20Although%20their%20devices%20had%20been%20seized%20in%20July%202019%20itself%2C%20the%20FSL%20report%20was%20received%20only%20this%20month%2C%20said%20the%20ATS.%3Cbr%3E%5CnSingh%20hails%20from%20Kushinagar%20in%20East%20UP%20and%20used%20to%20run%20an%20anti-fascist%20front.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20completing%20his%20education%20in%20polytechnic%20from%20Deoria%2C%20in%202004%20he%20started%20working%20in%20Raipur%20in%20Chhattisgarh%20with%20Rupantar%2C%20an%20NGO%20set%20up%20by%20activist%20Binayek%20Sen%20and%20his%20wife%20Ilina%20Sen.%20He%20met%20Binda%20in%20Raipur%20while%20working%20in%20the%20NGO%20and%20the%20two%20married.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ATS%20alleged%20that%20after%20getting%20married%20the%20two%20joined%20the%20CPI%20(Maoist)%20and%20in%202007-08%20came%20to%20Delhi%20but%20moved%20back%20to%20UP%20in%202009-10%20where%20they%20started%20organising%20work%20and%20propagating%20the%20Maoist%20ideology%20among%20farmers%2C%20labourers%20and%20students%20in%20the%20rural%20areas%20of%20Deoria%20and%20Kushinagar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESingh%20was%20arrested%20in%202010%20over%20an%20FIR%20lodged%20in%20Kanpur%20that%20linked%20him%20and%20several%20other%20activists%2C%20including%20the%20current%20president%20of%20the%20People%E2%80%99s%20Union%20of%20Civil%20Liberties%20UP%20unit%20Seema%20Azad%2C%20to%20the%20banned%20CPI%20(Maoist)%20and%20for%20allegedly%20possessing%20Maoist%20literature.%20He%20got%20bail%20in%202016.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ATS%20alleged%20that%20after%20being%20released%20from%20jail%2C%20Singh%20and%20his%20wife%20Binda%20again%20got%20involved%20in%20Naxalite%20activities%2C%20working%20with%20the%20top%20officials%20of%20the%20central%20committee%20and%20political%20bureau%20of%20the%20CPI%20(Maoist)%20in%20the%20%E2%80%9C2U%20region%E2%80%9D%20of%20the%20organization%20(UP%20and%20North%20Bihar).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ATS%20makes%20a%20specific%20allegation%20against%20the%20couple%2C%20accusing%20them%20of%20providing%20shelter%20to%20a%20wanted%20Naxal%20leader%20K.%20Srinivas%20alias%20Arvindji%20in%20Maharajganj%20in%202017-18.%20Arvindji%20carried%20a%20bounty%20of%20Rs%205%20lakh%2C%20said%20police.%20The%20ATS%20alleged%20that%20the%20couple%20provided%20Srinivas%20with%20a%20pseudonym%20Arvindji%20and%20recruited%20him%20as%20a%20teacher%20to%20help%20him%20conceal%20his%20identity%20and%20evade%20arrest.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ATS%20had%20made%20a%20similar%20allegation%20against%20activist%20Prabha%20last%20year%20when%20she%20and%20her%20husband%20Kushwaha%20were%20arrested%20in%20connection%20with%20the%20same%202019%20FIR.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20Kushwaha%20is%20linked%20to%20the%20Mazdoor%20Kisan%20Ekta%20Manch%20of%C2%A0Deoria%2C%C2%A0Prabha%C2%A0is%20associated%20with%20the%20outfit%20Savitri%20Bai%20Phule%20Sangarsh%20Samiti.%20Like%20Singh%20and%20Binda%2C%20Kushwaha%20and%20Prabha%20too%20had%20met%20while%20working%20in%20Chhattisgarh%20in%202006%20and%20got%20married%20in%202010.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20December%209%2C%202023%2C%20the%20jailed%20Prabha%2C%20who%20was%204.5%20months%20pregnant%2C%20suffered%20a%20miscarriage%C2%A0%20and%20was%20admitted%20to%20a%20women%E2%80%99s%20government%20hospital%20in%20Lucknow.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ATS%20had%20in%20October%202023%20arrested%20Kushwaha%20from%20his%20native%20place%20in%20Deoria%20in%20East%20UP%20while%20Prabha%20was%20arrested%20from%20her%20maternal%20house%20in%20Raipur%20where%20she%20had%20intended%20to%20rest%20during%20the%20period%20of%20her%20pregnancy.%20This%20was%20the%20second%20miscarriage%20Prabha%20suffered%20within%20months.%20She%20suffers%20from%20a%20hyperthyroid%20condition%2C%20raising%20the%20chances%20of%20a%20high-risk%20pregnancy%20for%20her%2C%20her%20family%20had%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20two%20couples%20face%20charges%20under%20Sections%20120B%2C%20121A%2C%20419%2C%20420%2C%20467%2C%20468%20and%20471%20of%20the%20Indian%20Penal%20Code%20and%20Sections%2013%2C%2018%20and%2038%20of%20the%20Unlawful%20Activities%20(Prevention)%20Act.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ATS%20had%20last%20year%20claimed%20that%20from%20data%20extraction%20it%20found%20letters%20and%20literature%20from%20Prabha%E2%80%99s%20and%20Kushwaha%E2%80%99s%20electronic%20devices%20that%20were%20linked%20to%20the%20banned%20Maoist%20outfit%20PLGA%20(People%E2%80%99s%20Liberation%20Guerilla%20Army)%20and%20CPI%20(Maoist).%20The%20documents%20were%20related%20to%20these%20outfits%20building%20a%20strong%20party%20and%20organization%20for%20resistance%20against%20the%20Indian%20government%2C%20the%20police%20alleged.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20July%202019%2C%20the%20UP%20ATS%20had%20lodged%20an%20FIR%20against%20seven%20persons%2C%20all%20of%20them%20political%20and%20social%20activists.%20According%20to%20the%20FIR%2C%20the%20police%20alleged%20that%20suspected%20Naxalites%20had%20been%20holding%20meetings%20in%20the%20states%20of%20UP%2C%20Bihar%2C%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20and%20Rajasthan%20and%20were%20engaging%20in%20criminal%20conspiracy%20to%20instigate%20people%20for%20armed%20rebellion%20and%20making%20a%20plan%20for%20satta%20parivartan%20(change%20in%20government).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ATS%20had%20then%20arrested%20two%20out%20of%20the%20seven%20named%20persons%2C%20Manish%20Azad%20aka%20Manish%20Srivastava%20and%20his%20wife%20Anita%20Srivastava%20from%20their%20residence%20in%20Bhopal.%20The%20two%2C%20who%20have%20a%20record%20in%20translation%20and%20academic%20work%2C%20were%20later%20granted%20bail.%20Srivastava%20is%20the%20brother%20of%20the%20PUCL%20UP%20president%20Seema%20Azad.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20police%20had%20then%20conducted%20raids%20in%20Bhopal%2C%20Kanpur%2C%20Deoria%20and%20Kushinagar%2C%20and%20also%20seized%20several%20electronic%20devices%20and%20documents.%C2%A0%20Although%20police%20questioned%20Kushwaha%2C%20Prabha%2C%20Singh%20and%20Binda%2C%20they%20were%20not%20arrested%20in%202019%20for%20want%20of%20physical%20evidence%20but%20only%20years%20later%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20extraction%20of%20data%20from%20their%20electronic%20devices.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20August%202023%2C%20the%20National%20Investigation%20Agency%20conducted%20simultaneous%20searches%20at%20the%20residences%20and%20offices%20of%20several%20activists%2C%20including%20Seema%20Azad%2C%20students%20in%20various%20cities%20of%20eastern%20UP%20purportedly%20to%20look%20for%20their%20alleged%20connection%20with%20the%20CPI%20(Maoist).%C2%A0%20The%20NIA%20had%20also%20raided%20the%20residence%20of%20Singh%2C%20as%20it%20conducted%20similar%20searches%20in%20eight%20locations%20in%20Prayagraj%2C%20Deoria%2C%20Varanasi%2C%20Chandauli%20and%20Azamgarh%20and%20seized%20mobile%20phones%2C%20SIM%20cards%2C%20laptops%2C%20books%2C%20pamphlets%2C%20magazines%20and%20other%20publications.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeema%20Azad%20and%20her%20husband%20Vishwa%20Vijay%20were%20arrested%20in%202010%20on%20charges%20of%20being%20members%20of%20the%20CPI%20(Maoist)%20and%20after%20spending%20more%20than%20two%20years%20in%20jail%2C%20were%20convicted%20by%20a%20lower%20court%20and%20awarded%20life%20imprisonment%20in%202012.%20A%20division%20bench%20of%20the%20HC%20in%20August%202012%2C%20however%2C%20granted%20them%20bail.%20Singh%20was%20a%20co-accused%20in%20the%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709706543000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F06114305%2FFotoJet-7.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fup-police-arrests-another-activist-couple-for-naxal-links-5-years-after-seizing-electronic-devices%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22This%20is%20the%20second%20such%20event%20in%20less%20than%20five%20months%20when%20the%20Anti-Terrorist%20Squad%20of%20the%20police%20arrested%20an%20activist%20couple%20for%20alleged%20Naxal%20links%20merely%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20analysis%20of%20data%20extracted%20from%20their%20phones%20and%20laptops%20seized%20more%20than%20four%20years%20ago.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A8%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fup-police-arrests-another-activist-couple-for-naxal-links-5-years-after-seizing-electronic-devices%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%E2%80%98Couldn%E2%80%99t%20Dream%20Earlier%20So%