out%20the%20manner%20in%20which%20the%20party%20organisation%20is%20shaped%20and%20used.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20State%20Where%20Congress%20Model%20Is%20Different%3A%20Kerala%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20one%20state%20where%20the%20Congress%20organisation%20resembles%20that%20of%20cadre-based%20parties.%20And%20no%2C%20it%20is%20not%20Karnataka.%20It's%20Kerala.%20The%20reason%20is%20that%20the%20Congress%20organisation%20there%20evolved%20in%20response%20to%20the%20cadres%20of%20the%20CPI(M).%20They%20had%20to.%20It's%20how%20they%20survived%20-%20though%20today%20even%20in%20Kerala%2C%20the%20organisation%20has%20weakened%2C%20as%20the%20last%20assembly%20election%20showed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJust%20as%20the%20Congress%20evolved%20a%20new%20organisational%20structure%20in%20Kerala%20in%20response%20to%20the%20CPI(M)%2C%20it%20needs%20to%20do%20so%20nationally%20too%20in%20response%20to%20the%20post-2014%20version%20of%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ELearning%20From%20The%20BJP%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20today%20has%20such%20a%20formidable%20party%20organisation%20that%20we%20rarely%20hear%20of%20the%20role%20of%20the%20Rashtriya%20Swayamsewak%20Sangh%20(RSS)%20workers%20in%20the%20party's%20election%20campaigns%20anymore.%20It%20is%20well-known%20that%20the%20BJP%20has%20expanded%20its%20party%20organisation%20manifold%20since%202014.%20What%20is%20less%20appreciated%20is%20what%20this%20organisation%20does.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECritics%20and%20analysts%20focus%20on%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi's%20speeches%20and%20campaigns%2C%20as%20well%20as%20the%20media%2C%20as%20the%20factors%20behind%20the%20BJP's%20victories.%20But%20the%20huge%20army%20of%20party%20workers%20going%20from%20door%20to%20door%20does%20not%20get%20credit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20common%20man%20cannot%20reach%20Narendra%20Modi%20or%20Rahul%20Gandhi.%20For%20the%20common%20man%2C%20the%20party%20is%20the%20party%20worker%20who%20lives%20next%20door.%20The%20party%20worker%20does%20what%20she%20can%20for%20the%20people%20living%20in%20her%20polling%20booth%2C%20all%20year%20round.%20As%20a%20result%2C%20it's%20the%20party%20worker%20who%20can%20pull%20in%20the%20BJP%20vote%20as%20a%20personal%20favour.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EBJP's%20Tech-Savvy%20Army%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20has%20always%20been%20true%20of%20political%20parties.%20Apart%20from%20increasing%20the%20number%20of%20party%20workers%20to%20a%20massive%2020%20per%20booth%2C%20the%20BJP%20has%20centralised%20and%20turbo-charged%20this%20army%20with%20technology.%20Party%20workers%20are%20given%20regular%20campaign%20tasks%2C%20at%20least%20once%20a%20month%2C%20to%20reach%20every%20home.%20Whether%20it's%20G20%20or%20Ram%20Mandir%20or%20free%20food%20grains%2C%20the%20party%20worker%20will%20take%20the%20message%20to%20every%20doorstep.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20the%20BJP%20still%20loses%20some%20state%20elections%2C%20it%20is%20because%20in%20a%20given%20situation%2C%20the%20party%20may%20suffer%20narrative%20issues%2C%20such%20as%20indefensible%20anti-incumbency%20or%20leadership%20challenges%2C%20say%2C%20a%20lightweight%20chief%20minister.%20But%20even%20in%20such%20scenarios%2C%20the%20BJP%20invariably%20retains%20a%20strong%20vote%20share%2C%20thanks%20to%20the%20workers%20who%20bring%20in%20the%20vote.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20workers%20are%20answerable%20for%20their%20tasks%20to%20the%20party%20leadership%20centrally%2C%20and%20not%20to%20local%20leaders.%20The%20BJP%20manages%20this%20centralisation%20through%20technology.%20These%20days%2C%20the%20party%20uses%20an%20app%20called%20'Saral'%2C%20where%20workers%20have%20to%20upload%20selfies%20to%20prove%20that%20they%20actually%20organised%20a%20small%20gathering%20to%20make%20people%20hear%20the%20fortnightly%20episode%20of%20PM%20Modi's%20%3Cem%3EMann%20Ki%20Baat%20%3C%2Fem%3Eshow.%20If%20a%20worker%20doesn't%20perform%20well%2C%20she%20can%20be%20replaced%20-%20after%20all%2C%20there%20is%20no%20dearth%20of%20cadres%20in%20the%20party.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Risk%20Of%20Shifting%20Loyalties%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%20contrast%2C%20the%20lone%20Congress%20worker%20in%20a%20polling%20booth%20is%20answerable%20to%20the%20local%20Congress%20leader.%20If%20the%20Congress%20leader%20switches%20to%20the%20BJP%2C%20so%20does%20the%20worker%20and%20the%20votes%20she%20possibly%20commands.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20no%20reason%20why%20the%20Congress%20should%20not%20or%20cannot%20create%20a%20new%20centralised%20party%20organisation%20like%20the%20BJP's.%20In%20fact%2C%20I'll%20go%20a%20step%20further%20and%20say%20that%20the%20Congress%20party's%20long-term%20revival%20is%20impossible%20unless%20it%20creates%20a%20new%20tech-driven%20centralised%20party%20organisation%20where%20workers%20are%20held%20accountable%20for%20door-to-door%20campaigning%20through%20technology.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt's%20not%20a%20question%20of%20%3Cem%3Eif%2C%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3Ebut%20%3Cem%3Ewhen%3C%2Fem%3E.%20Now%20is%20a%20good%20time%20to%20begin.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Naresh%20Arora%20is%20an%20accomplished%20political%20strategist.%20He%20has%20worked%20for%20the%20Congress%20party%20for%20Haryana%2C%20Assam%2C%20Karnataka%20and%20Rajasthan%20Assembly%20elections)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709706000000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.ndtvimg.com%2Fi%2F2018-03%2Fbjp-flags-650_650x400_71520085058.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fcongress-revival-is-impossible-without-a-cadre-based-model-5185775%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20common%20man%20cannot%20reach%20Narendra%20Modi%20or%20Rahul%20Gandhi.%20For%20the%20common%20man%2C%20the%20party%20is%20the%20party%20worker%20who%20lives%20next%20door.%20The%20BJP%20seems%20to%20understand%20this%20well.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fcongress-revival-is-impossible-without-a-cadre-based-model-5185775%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fcongress-revival-is-impossible-without-a-cadre-based-model-5185775%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fcongress-revival-is-impossible-without-a-cadre-based-model-5185775%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22EST%20N8%20Hires%20Chatsuree%20Sripamorn%20for%20Asian%20Sales%20Role%20Ahead%20of%20FilMart%20Debut%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709704800000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FChatsuree-Sripamorn-IMG_9655-lcr-res.jpg%3Fw%3D1000%26h%3D563%26crop%3D1%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F%3Fp%3D1235926373%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22EST%20N8%2C%20the%20film%20and%20TV%20sales%20venture%20formed%20by%20U.S.-based%20EST%20and%20Thailand%E2%80%99s%20N8%20company%2C%20has%20hired%20Chatsuree%20%E2%80%98Chat%E2%80%99%20Sripamorn%20for%20an%20Asian%20sales%20roles.%20Reporting%20to%20Tenten%20Wei%2C%20she%20will%20represent%20the%20company%20at%20next%20week%E2%80%99s%20FilMart.%20Sripamorn%20has%20previously%20worked%20at%20three%20of%20the%20top%20Thai%20entertainment%20companies%20Mono%20Next%2C%20GMM%20Studios%20%5B%E2%80%A6%5D%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Patrick%20Frater%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F2024%2Ffilm%2Fnews%2Fest-n8-chatsuree-sripamorn-asia-sales-filmart-1235926373%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fvariety.com%2F2024%2Ffilm%2Fnews%2Fest-n8-chatsuree-sripamorn-asia-sales-filmart-1235926373%2Famp%2F%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F2024%2Ffilm%2Fnews%2Fest-n8-chatsuree-sripamorn-asia-sales-filmart-1235926373%2Famp%2F%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Watch%20%7C%20'Arambai%20Tenggol%20is%20Biren%20Singh's%20Creation%20to%20Threaten%20Centre%3B%20Today%20It's%20More%20Important%20Than%20Govt'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F06111311%2FKT-6-March-2.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20an%20interview%20to%20discuss%20how%20Manipur%E2%80%99s%20Kuki%20community%20view%20recent%20developments%20in%20the%20northeastern%20state%2C%20one%20of%20the%20most%20highly%20regarded%20Kuki%20politicians%2C%20who%20is%20also%20a%20BJP%20MLA%2C%20has%20said%20that%20the%20Arambai%20Tenggol%20is%20a%20creation%20of%20Biren%20Singh%20and%20Sanajaoba%2C%20the%20former%20ruler%20of%20Manipur%2C%20and%20it%20has%20%E2%80%9Cbeen%20created%20to%20preserve%20the%20chief%20minister%E2%80%99s%20position%20for%20Biren%20Singh%E2%80%9D.%20Paolienlal%20Haokip%20added%20that%20Biren%20Singh%20uses%20the%20Arambai%20Tenggol%20to%20threaten%20the%20Centre.%20Haokip%20also%20said%20that%20today%20the%20Arambai%20Tenggol%20is%20more%20important%20than%20the%20state%20government.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20about%20the%20BJP%2C%20of%20which%20he%20is%20a%20member%2C%20Haokip%20made%20crystal%20clear%20the%20sharp%20and%20deep%20differences%20between%20him%20and%20the%20chief%20minister.%20He%20says%20he%E2%80%99s%20raised%20these%20issues%20with%20the%20Home%20Minister%20(Amit%20Shah)%20but%20got%20no%20response.%20He%20added%20that%2C%20sadly%2C%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20has%20not%20found%20time%20to%20speak%20to%20any%20of%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20Kuki%20MLAs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22allowfullscreen%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2F-hIHyH-zMgE%3Fsi%3Djauo4rjecNJQxC2_%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22100%25%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22504%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%20data-mce-type%3D%5C%22bookmark%5C%22%3E%EF%BB%BF%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Haokip%20made%20clear%20that%20he%20would%20not%20resign%20from%20the%20BJP%20because%20he%E2%80%99s%20determined%20to%20fight%20for%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20future.%20At%20the%20moment%2C%20he%20said%2C%20the%20BJP%20in%20Manipur%20has%20been%20appropriated%20by%20a%20particular%20ethnic%20group%2C%20by%20which%20he%20meant%20the%20Meiteis.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20am%20only%20identifying%20the%20key%20main%20points.%20There%20are%20many%20others%20but%20I%20think%20you%20should%20hear%20them%20from%20Haokip%20himself.%20I%20do%20not%20want%20to%20run%20the%20risk%20of%20conveying%20the%20wrong%20impression%20of%20his%20views%20through%20a%20precis%20or%20paraphrase.%20He%20has%20been%20courageous%20and%20outspoken%2C%20no%20doubt%20at%20considerable%20cost%20to%20himself%2C%20and%20I%20do%20not%20want%20to%20even%20inadvertently%20add%20to%20his%20problems%20by%20conveying%20the%20wrong%20impression%20of%20his%20position.%20So%20please%20watch%20this%20interview%20yourself.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20I%20will%20give%20you%20the%20list%20of%20questions%20asked%20which%20were%20followed%20meticulously.%20They%20will%20indicate%20the%20issues%20raised%20and%20help%20you%20understand%20the%20interview.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHere%20are%20the%20questions%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E1)%20The%20Manipur%20Assembly%20has%20passed%20a%20resolution%20calling%20upon%20the%20central%20government%20%E2%80%9Cto%20completely%20abrogate%20the%20SoO%20pact%20with%20all%20the%20Kuki-Zo%20militant%20groups%E2%80%9D.%20It%20wants%20this%20done%20%E2%80%9Cin%20the%20interest%20of%20ensuring%20peace%20and%20security%20in%20the%20region%E2%80%9D.%20As%20a%20member%20of%20the%20Assembly%20and%20as%20a%20member%20of%20the%20BJP%20how%20do%20you%20respond%20to%20this%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E2)%20In%20his%20message%20on%20X%20Chief%20Minister%20Biren%20Singh%20claimed%20the%20resolution%20was%20passed%20%E2%80%9Cunanimously%E2%80%9D.%20But%20if%20all%20ten%20Kuki-Zo%20MLAs%20were%20not%20present%20in%20the%20Assembly%20is%20he%20correct%20to%20call%20it%20unanimous%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E3)%20How%20did%20the%20ten%20Naga%20MLAs%20vote%3F%20I%20presume%20they%20were%20present%20and%20voted%20in%20favour.%20Am%20I%20right%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAre%20differences%20between%20the%20Kuki-Zo%20and%20the%20Nagas%20emerging%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E4)%20Now%20in%20a%20press%20release%20that%20the%20ten%20Kuki%20MLAs%20issued%20you%20pointed%20out%20that%20a%20Joint%20Monitoring%20Group%20exists%20to%20oversee%20the%20agreement.%20In%20your%20press%20release%20you%20asked%3A%20%E2%80%9CWe%20would%20like%20to%20question%20whether%20the%20resolution%20adopted%20by%20the%20august%20House%20was%20passed%20on%20any%20report%20or%20observations%20of%20the%20JMG%2C%20which%20is%20the%20only%20official%20mechanism%20to%20determine%20whether%20any%20violation%20of%20the%20ground%20rules%20has%20taken%20place%20or%20not.%E2%80%9D%20What%E2%80%99s%20your%20answer%20to%20that%20question%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E5)%20Days%20after%20this%20resolution%20calling%20for%20the%20abrogation%20of%20the%20SoO%20agreement%2C%20the%20Manipur%20Assembly%20reaffirmed%20an%20earlier%20resolution%20of%202022%20calling%20for%20the%20implementation%20of%20the%20National%20Register%20of%20Citizens%20in%20Manipur.%20How%20do%20you%20respond%20to%20that%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E6)%20In%20his%20message%20on%20X%20this%20is%20what%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20said%3A%20%E2%80%9CNRC%20is%20crucial%20for%20safeguarding%20the%20interests%20of%20our%20state%20and%20contributing%20to%20the%20greater%20good%20of%20our%20nation.%E2%80%9D%20He%E2%80%99s%20your%20party%20leader.%20How%20do%20you%20respond%20to%20that%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E7)%20The%20paradox%20is%20whilst%20the%20Biren%20Singh%20government%20is%20pushing%20to%20scrap%20the%20SoO%20agreements%20it%E2%80%99s%20also%20allowing%20the%20Arambai%20Tenggol%20to%20become%20a%20law%20unto%20themselves%20and%20defy%20the%20police.%20A%20recent%20statement%20by%20the%20police%20accuses%20Arambai%20Tenggol%20of%20%E2%80%9Cmany%20anti-social%20activities%20such%20as%20assaulting%20civilians%20and%20snatching%20vehicles%E2%80%9D.%20The%20police%20also%20say%20they%20are%20%E2%80%9Cinvolved%20in%20extortion%E2%80%9D.%20Last%20month%20the%20Tenggol%20abducted%20an%20Additional%20Superintendent%20of%20Police%20because%20its%20Sekmai%20unit%20Chief%20was%20arrested%20for%20allegedly%20snatching%20a%20vehicle%20from%20a%20petrol%20pump.%20How%20do%20you%20respond%20to%20all%20of%20this%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E8)%20The%20police%20have%20told%20The%20Hindu%20that%20%E2%80%9Cour%20hands%20are%20tied.%20We%20are%20stopped%20from%20taking%20action%20against%20the%20miscreants.%E2%80%9D%20Why%20is%20your%20Chief%20Minister%20not%20acting%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E9)%20A%20second%20worrying%20development%20concerns%20the%20United%20National%20Liberation%20Front.%20After%20they%20signed%20a%20peace%20agreement%20in%20November%2C%20it%20was%20intended%20they%20would%20be%20kept%20in%20camps%20and%20monitored%20by%20central%20agencies.%20But%20The%20Hindu%20says%20they%20are%20roaming%20around%20in%20vehicles%2C%20brandishing%20weapons%2C%20indulging%20in%20violence%20against%20security%20forces%20and%20looting%20police%20armouries.%20Once%20again%2C%20why%20has%20your%20Chief%20Minister%20not%20done%20anything%20to%20stop%20this%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E10)%20It%20seems%20as%20if%20Biren%20Singh%20has%20two%20aims%20%E2%80%93%20to%20scupper%20the%20SoO%20agreement%2C%20which%20would%20upset%20the%20Kuki-Zo%20community%2C%20and%20give%20a%20free%20hand%20to%20Arambai%20Tenggol%20and%20UNLF%2C%20which%20would%20please%20the%20Meitei%20community.%20Am%20I%20mistaken%20or%20am%20I%20right%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E11)%20Let%E2%80%99s%20focus%20on%20you%20before%20we%20end.%20You%20have%20sharp%20differences%20with%20Biren%20Singh%20and%20your%20Meitei%20colleagues%20in%20the%20BJP.%20Why%20have%20you%20not%20resigned%20from%20the%20BJP%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E12)%20Have%20you%20raised%20your%20concerns%20directly%20with%20Amit%20Shah%3F%20And%20if%20you%20have%2C%20what%E2%80%99s%20the%20answer%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709704773000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F06111311%2FKT-6-March-2.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fvideo%2Fwatch-arambai-tenggol-is-biren-singhs-creation-to-threaten-centre-today-its-more-important-than-govt%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20an%20interview%20to%20Karan%20Thapar%2C%20BJP%20MLA%20from%20Manipur%2C%20Paolienlal%20Haokip%2C%20discusses%20how%20Kuki%20community%20view%20recent%20developments%20in%20the%20state.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fvideo%2Fwatch-arambai-tenggol-is-biren-singhs-creation-to-threaten-centre-today-its-more-important-than-govt%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%2210%20million%20Thais%20had%20smog-related%20illness%20in%202023%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709704584000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2F12A6%2Fproduction%2F_132847740_9d96c3ae51b14b10c006acc6c8c10574503470bd-1.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-asia-68487230%231%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Toxic%20smog%20from%20burning%20farms%20shroud%20large%20swathes%20of%20Thailand%20at%20the%20beginning%20of%20every%20year.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A45%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-asia-68487230%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-bbc-co-uk.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-asia-68487230.amp%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-asia-68487230.amp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22We're%20on%20course%20for%20the%20oldest%20presidential%20race%20in%20US%20h