ion.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EJustice%20Deepak%20Gupta%20said%20the%20SBI%E2%80%99s%20position%20was%20%E2%80%9Cabsolutely%20ridiculous%E2%80%9D%20and%20highlighted%20the%20Supreme%20Court%E2%80%99s%20role%20now%20in%20ensuring%20that%20people%20get%20to%20know%20what%20they%20have%20the%20right%20to%20know.%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EBelow%20is%20the%20full%20text%20of%20the%2015-minute%20interview%2C%20edited%20lightly%20for%20coherence%20and%20style.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EKaran%20Thapar%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cspan%3E%3A%20Hello%20and%20welcome%20to%20a%20special%20interview%20for%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E.%20Just%20as%20we%20were%20preparing%20ourselves%20to%20receive%20critical%20details%20and%20information%20about%20electoral%20bonds%3B%20who%20bought%20them%2C%20who%20they%20were%20paid%20to%2C%20what%20was%20the%20sum%20involved%2C%20it%20seems%20the%20State%20Bank%20of%20India%20has%20thrown%20a%20spanner%20in%20the%20works.%20In%20a%20petition%20to%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20is%20requested%20for%20more%20than%20three%20and%20a%20half%20months%20extra%20time%2C%20making%20clear%20it%20cannot%20provide%20the%20information%20till%20the%2030th%20of%20June.%20If%20that%E2%80%99s%20agreed%20to%2C%20the%20information%20will%20only%20come%20into%20the%20public%20domain%20after%20the%20elections%20are%20over.%20Joining%20me%20now%20to%20share%20his%20first%20response%20to%20this%20development%2C%20is%20one%20of%20the%20most%20highly%20regarded%20former%20judges%20of%20our%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20Justice%20Deepak%20Gupta.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EJustice%20Gupta%2C%20on%20the%2015th%20of%20February%2C%20when%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20passed%20what%E2%80%99s%20come%20to%20be%20commonly%20called%20%E2%80%98The%20Electoral%20Bonds%20Judgment%E2%80%99%2C%20it%20ordered%20the%20State%20Bank%20of%20India%20to%20hand%20over%20relevant%20details%20of%20electoral%20bonds%3B%20their%20amounts%2C%20who%20they%20were%20bought%20by%2C%20and%20who%20were%20they%20paid%20to%2C%20to%20the%20election%20commission%20by%20the%206th%20of%20March.%20In%20response%2C%20the%20State%20Bank%20of%20India%20has%20filed%20a%20petition%20seeking%20more%20than%20three%20months%20extra%20time%2C%20till%20the%2030th%20of%20June.%20Let%20me%20start%20by%20asking%2C%20as%20a%20former%20judge%20of%20the%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20how%20do%20you%20respond%20to%20this%20development%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EJustice%20Deepak%20Gupta%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cspan%3E%3A%20See%2C%20this%20order%20of%20the%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20this%20specific%20order%2C%20directing%20the%20SBI%2C%20State%20Bank%20of%20India%2C%20to%20furnish%20the%20information%2C%20is%20in%20respect%20to%20an%20earlier%20order%20passed%20on%2012th%20April%202019%3B%20when%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20had%20directed%20them%20to%20keep%2C%20maintain%20these%20records.%20And%20from%20the%20application%2C%20what%20I%E2%80%99ve%20seen%20of%20the%20application%2C%20they%20say%20there%20are%2022%2C000%20such%20bonds%2C%20and%20they%E2%80%99ve%20maintained%20records%20of%2022%2C000%20at%20one%20end%20and%20%E2%80%93%20this%20is%20just%2044%2C000.%20I%E2%80%99m%20sure%20these%20records%20have%20been%20maintained%20both%20physically%20and%20digitally.%20I%20think%20it%20should%20take%20a%20few%20hours%2C%20or%20a%20few%20days%20at%20the%20most%2C%20to%20collate%20all%20the%20records.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EKT%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cspan%3E%3A%20You%E2%80%99re%20saying%20it%20should%20take%20a%20few%20hours%2C%20or%20a%20few%20days%20at%20the%20most%3B%20they%20don%E2%80%99t%20need%20time%20till%20the%2030th%20of%20June.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EDG%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cspan%3E%3A%20Yeah%2C%20I%20mean%20their%20application%20itself%20says%20that%20there%20are%20only%2022%2C000%20bonds%20sold%20after%20the%20April%202019%20order.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EKT%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cspan%3E%3A%20The%20other%20important%20thing%20is%2C%20you%20said%20the%20April%202019%20order%20from%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20had%20told%20the%20SBI%20to%20keep%20a%20record%20of%20bonds%2C%20therefore%20this%20record%20should%20already%20be%20there.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EDG%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cspan%3E%3A%20Yeah%2C%20in%20my%20view%2C%20I%20think%20I%20was%20a%20part%20of%20the%20bench%20which%20passed%20the%20order%20directing%20them%20to%3B%20it%20was%20headed%20by%20Justice%20Gogoi%2C%20and%20I%20think%20they%20had%20to%20maintain%20the%20records.%20Now%20they%20can%20maintain%20it%20secretly%2C%20they%20may%20be%20right%20that%20they%E2%80%99ve%20maintained%20in%20such%20a%20fashion%20so%20as%20not%20to%20disclose%20the%20anonymity%20which%20was%20required%20under%20the%20law%20as%20it%20then%20stored%2C%20but%20they%20were%20required%20to%20maintain%20records%20and%20it%20shouldn%E2%80%99t%20take%20three%20months%20time%20to%20collate%20the%20records.%20It%20should%20take%20a%20few%20days.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FL-qdDu1N3i8%3Ffeature%3Doembed%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22840%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22%E2%80%9CI%20Don%E2%80%99t%20Believe%20SBI%E2%80%99s%20Explanation%20on%20Electoral%20Bonds%3B%20it%E2%80%99s%20Absolutely%20Ridiculous%E2%80%9D%3A%20Former%20SC%20Judge%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22473%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EKT%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cspan%3E%3A%20Absolutely.%20Since%20they%20were%20ordered%20by%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20in%202019%20to%20maintain%20records%2C%20those%20records%20have%20clearly%20been%20maintained%2C%20they%20need%20to%20be%20collated%2C%20they%20need%20to%20be%20made%20public%2C%20and%20it%20shouldn%E2%80%99t%20take%20three%20and%20a%20half%20months%2C%20beyond%20the%20time%20limit%20set.%20Let%E2%80%99s%20forget%20they%20already%20had%20three%20weeks%2C%20it%20shouldn%E2%80%99t%20take%20an%20additional%20three%20and%20a%20half%20months%20for%20them%20to%20do%20this.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EDG%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cspan%3E%3A%20Yeah%2C%20I%20agree.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EKT%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cspan%3E%3A%20In%20other%20words%2C%20you%20don%E2%80%99t%20accept%20the%20explanation%20they%E2%80%99re%20giving%2C%20and%20for%20the%20sake%20of%20the%20audience%20I%E2%80%99ll%20repeat%20that%20explanation%3B%20they%E2%80%99re%20saying%20they%20have%2044%2C434%20sets%20of%20information%2C%20which%20they%20claim%20are%20kept%20in%20two%20different%20silos.%20They%20also%20claim%20secondly%2C%20that%20some%20of%20this%20information%20is%20digitally%20stored%20and%20some%20is%20physically%20stored.%20You%E2%80%99re%20saying%20none%20of%20that%20should%20lead%20to%20the%20conclusion%20that%20they%20need%20three%20and%20a%20half%20months%20more%20till%20the%2030th%20of%20June.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EDG%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cspan%3E%3A%20See%20the%20same%20application%20says%20that%20the%20total%20number%20of%20bonds%20sold%20after%20April%2012%2C%202019%20are%2022%2C217.%20So%20they%20say%20half%20the%20information%20was%20kept%20at%20one%20place%2C%20and%20half%20at%20another.%20So%20the%20information%20becomes%20double%2C%20with%20regard%20to%2022%2C000%20bonds%20only%2C%2022%2C000-odd%20bonds.%20But%20that%20means%E2%80%A6what%20of%20the%20information%20on%20the%2044%2C000%20bonds%3F%20Even%20if%20they%20kept%20at%20two%20different%20places%2C%20and%20once%20the%20court%20had%20directed%20that%20they%20have%20to%20keep%20this%20information%2C%20it%20was%20the%20bounding%20duty%20to%20keep%20it%20in%20such%20a%20manner%20that%20when%20the%20court%20asks%20them%20to%20disclose%20it%2C%20they%20should%20disclose%20it%20as%20early%20as%20possible%2C%20not%20that%20they%20take%20months%20to%20disclose%20it.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EKT%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cspan%3E%3A%20Which%20means%20that%20by%20their%20explanation%20that%20they%E2%80%99ve%20given%20the%20court%2C%20they%E2%80%99ve%20either%20been%20negligent%20and%20haven%E2%80%99t%20followed%20court%20orders%20%E2%80%93%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EDG%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cspan%3E%3A%20No%2C%20I%20think%2C%20I%20mean%20I%20can%E2%80%99t%20prejudge%2C%20I%20mean%20the%20court%E2%80%99s%20important%2C%20but%20in%20my%20opinion%20this%20explanation%20is%20not%20really%20worth%20much.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EKT%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cspan%3E%3A%20Now%20in%20its%20petition%2C%20and%20I%E2%80%99m%20quoting%20the%20version%20of%20the%20petition%20published%20by%20the%20Indian%20Express%20today%2C%20the%20State%20Bank%20of%20India%20cites%20Clause%2074%20of%20the%20Electoral%20Bond%20scheme%20of%202018.%20That%20clause%20says%2C%20and%20I%E2%80%99m%20quoting%20%E2%80%98the%20information%20furnished%20by%20the%20buyer%2C%20shall%20be%20treated%20as%20confidential%20except%E2%80%99%2C%20and%20this%20is%20the%20important%20part%2C%20%E2%80%98except%20when%20demanded%20by%20a%20competent%20court%2C%20or%20any%20law%20enforcement%20agency%E2%80%99.%20So%20their%20very%20scheme%20requires%20that%20the%20information%20should%20be%20made%20available%20to%20a%20competent%20court%20whenever%20required%2C%20at%20least%20the%20information%20about%20who%20bought%20the%20bonds%2C%20and%20what%20they%20were%20worth.%20So%20clearly%20now%20they%20can%E2%80%99t%20claim%20that%20they%20need%20three%20and%20a%20half%20months%20to%20put%20it%20together.%20If%20a%20competent%20court%20had%20asked%20them%20for%20this%20information%20a%20year%20or%20two%20or%20three%20earlier%2C%20they%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20have%20turned%20around%20and%20said%2C%20%E2%80%98Sorry%20sir%20it%E2%80%99s%20going%20to%20take%20us%20four%20months%20to%20give%20it%20to%20you%E2%80%99.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EDG%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cspan%3E%3A%20No%2C%20I%E2%80%99m%20clearly%20of%20the%20view%20that%2C%20you%20see%20what%20happened%20was%20that%20the%20court%20said%20that%20time%20%E2%80%93%20there%20was%20not%20enough%20time%20left%20to%20go%20into%20the%20merits%20of%20the%20case%20on%20the%20electoral%20bonds%2C%20and%20elections%20were%20coming%2C%20so%20the%20court%20had%20ordered%20that%20please%20keep%20a%20record%20of%20everything.%20Now%20when%20the%20court%20orders%20you%20to%20keep%20a%20record%2C%20you%20must%20maintain%20it%20in%20a%20manner%20that%20when%20the%20court%20asks%20you%20to%20give%20the%20record%2C%20you%20don%E2%80%99t%20turn%20around%20and%20say%20%E2%80%98now%20it%20will%20take%20us%20three-and-a-half%2C%20four%20months%20time%20to%20give%20it.%20I%E2%80%99m%20very%20clear%20of%20the%20view%20they%20can%E2%80%99t.%20And%20this%20explanation%20also%2C%2044%2C000%20%E2%80%93%20Mr%20Thapar%2C%20in%20today%E2%80%99s%20day%20and%20age%20this%20bank%20must%20be%20dealing%20with%20millions%2C%20maybe%2044%20million%20entries%20a%20day%2C%20in%20its%20different%20branches%20all%20over%20the%20country.%20And%20to%20say%20that%20it%20requires%20three%20and%20a%20half%20months%20to%20collate%2044%2C000%20records%2C%20in%20my%20view%20is%20just%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20absolutely%20ludicrous.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EKT%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cspan%3E%3A%20Absolutely%20ridiculous%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EDG%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cspan%3E%3A%20Yeah.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EKT%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cspan%3E%3A%20A%20lot%20of%20people%2C%20Justice%20Gupta%2C%20have%20come%20to%20the%20prima%20facie%20conclusion%2C%20that%20the%20State%20Bank%20of%20India%20has%20requested%20extra%20time%20because%20it%20wants%20to%20deliberately%20delay%20making%20the%20information%20public%20until%20the%20elections%20are%20over.%20In%20turn%2C%20this%20seems%20to%20suggest%20that%20what%20they%20have%20could%20be%20incriminating%20and%20potentially%20embarrassing%2C%20very%20possibly%20or%20very%20particularly%2C%20for%20the%20government%20in%20part.%20Is%20that%20a%20fair%20inference%20for%20people%20to%20draw%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EKDG%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cspan%3E%3A%20See%20I%20would%20not%20like%20to%20speculate%2C%20I%20mean%20I%E2%80%99m%20not%20a%20political%20animal%20either%2C%20but%20having%20said%20that%20when%20elections%20%E2%80%93%20please%20remember%2C%20what%20is%20the%20basis%20of%20this%20judgement%20declaring%20the%20Electoral%20bonds%20to%20be%20illegal%3F%20The%20basis%20of%20this%20judgement%2C%20especially%20Justice%20Sanjiv%20Khanna%E2%80%99s%20analysis%2C%20is%20that%20the%20public%20have%20a%20right%20to%20know%20who%20has%20contributed%20to%20whom.%20And%20if%20this%20application%20is%20allowed%2C%20then%20it%20will%20scuttle%20the%20very%20basis%20of%20that%20judgement.%20Then%20the%20people%20will%20not%20know%20who%20has%20contributed%20to%20which%20party%2C%20before%20the%20elections.%20I%20think%2C%20even%20if%20time%20is%20extended%2C%20it%20should%20not%20be%20extended%20to%20any%20period%20beyond%20the%20date%2C%20before%20elections%20are%20held.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EKT%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cspan%3E%3A%20But%20you%E2%80%99re%20saying%20a%20very%20important%20thing%2C%20you%E2%80%99re%20saying%20if%20the%20petition%20requesting%20additional%20time%20till%20the%2030th%20of%20June%20is%20agreed%20to%20%E2%80%93%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EDG%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cspan%3E%3A%20Partly.%20I%E2%80%99m%20not%20saying%20it%20should%2C%20even%20if%20some%20time%20has%20to%20be%20granted.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EKT%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cspan%3E%3A%20But%20it%20must%20not%20be%20till%20after%20the%20elections%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EDG%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cspan%3E%3A%20Till%20the%20polling%2C%20in%20fact%20I%20should%20say%20till%20the%20polling%20is%20said%2C%20it%20should%20be%20before%20the%20polling%2C%20it%20should%20be%20declared.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EKT%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cspan%3E%3A%20Because%20otherwise%20it%20will%20effectively%20scuttle%20Justice%20Khanna%E2%80%99s%20judgement%20that%20people%20have%20a%20right%20%E2%80%93%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EDG%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cspan%3E%3A%20