0Sheldon%20Pollock%20two%20years%20ago.%20Though%20turmoil%20within%20the%20remaining%20team%20has%20been%20suspected%20for%20some%20time%2C%20the%20statement%20%E2%80%93%20signed%20by%20Whitney%20Cox%20(University%20of%20Chicago)%2C%20Maria%20Heim%20(Amherst%20College)%2C%20Rajeev%20Kinra%20(Northwestern%20University)%2C%20Francesca%20Orsini%20(SOAS%2C%20University%20of%20London)%2C%20and%20Archana%20Venkatesan%20(University%20of%20California%2C%20Davis)%20%E2%80%93%20marks%20the%20first%20public%20evidence%20of%20internal%20dissonance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20the%20statement%2C%20the%20former%20board%20members%20pointed%20out%20how%20the%20library%20has%20been%20without%20a%20general%20editor%20since%202022%20after%20the%20founding%20general%20editor%2C%20Professor%20Sheldon%20Pollock%2C%20was%20%E2%80%9Cforced%20to%20resign%2C%20also%20with%20no%20reason%20given%2C%20two%20years%20before%20his%20planned%20retirement%E2%80%9D.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F06090320%2FGH17G2vXcAAlK67-956x1024.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22840%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F06090320%2FGH17G2vXcAAlK67-956x1024.png%20956w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F06090320%2FGH17G2vXcAAlK67-280x300.png%20280w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F06090320%2FGH17G2vXcAAlK67.png%201094w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-700324%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EThe%20statement%20by%20the%20five%20MCLI%20members.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CProf.%20Patil%20determined%20that%20no%20successor%20would%20be%20appointed.%20We%20repeatedly%20expressed%20concern%20not%20only%20about%20that%20decision%20and%20its%20likely%20effect%20on%20the%20series%2C%20but%20about%20the%20lack%20of%20transparency%20in%20decision-making%2C%20in%20the%20acquisition%20and%20approval%20of%20new%20projects%2C%20and%20in%20the%20issuing%20of%20contracts%3B%20and%20about%20the%20opaque%20and%20uncollegial%20management%20style%20of%20Prof.%20Patil%20and%20Harvard%20University%20Press%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20statement%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20the%20last%20eighteen%20months%2C%20even%20as%20the%20roles%20and%20responsibilities%20of%20the%20editorial%20board%20became%20increasingly%20unclear%2C%20and%20communication%20with%20Prof.%20Patil%20effectively%20stopped%2C%20we%20worked%20tirelessly%20with%20translators%20on%20their%20book%20manuscripts%2C%E2%80%9D%20it%20added.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20academics%20also%20questioned%20the%20future%20of%20the%20translation%20work%20currently%20underway%20and%20said%20that%20there%20has%20been%20no%20communication%20from%20the%20board%20or%20the%20university%20press%20regarding%20the%20direction%20the%20library%20will%20take.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20statement%20said%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CTogether%20we%20were%20responsible%20for%20editing%20and%20supervising%20the%20translation%20and%20publication%20of%2043%20books%20under%20contract%2C%20in%20Apabhramsha%2C%20Bangla%2C%20Hindi%20(Brajbhasha%20and%20Avadhi)%2C%20Kannada%2C%20Pali%2C%20Panjabi%2C%20Persian%2C%20Sanskrit%2C%20Tamil%2C%20Telugu%2C%20and%20Urdu.%20Who%20is%20to%20undertake%20this%20work%20in%20the%20future%20and%20what%20is%20to%20become%20of%20the%20translations%20currently%20being%20edited%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20has%20been%20no%20further%20communication%20from%20the%20Board%20or%20the%20Press%3B%20in%20particular%2C%20there%20has%20been%20no%20notion%20of%20the%20future%20direction%20of%20the%20Library%20or%20of%20the%20status%20of%20works%20already%20under%20contract.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20academics%20also%20wrote%20to%20the%20Provost%20of%20Harvard%20University%2C%20the%20ultimate%20authority%20over%20all%20appointments%20to%20the%20editorial%20and%20oversight%20Boards%2C%20to%20conduct%20an%20external%20review%20of%20these%20developments%20and%20the%20future%20of%20the%20series.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EProfessor%20Patil%2C%20while%20refraining%20from%20responding%20to%20the%20statement%2C%20said%20that%20the%20process%20of%20rebuilding%20the%20editorial%20board%20was%20underway%20with%20two%20new%20additions%20%E2%80%93%20Indian%20poet%20and%20art%20critic%20Ranjit%20Hoskote%20and%20renowned%20translator%20Mini%20Krishnan.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20the%20coming%20months%20we%20plan%20to%20add%20more%20editors%20to%20the%20board.%20We%20are%20deeply%20committed%20to%20the%20MCLI%20books%20under%20contract%20and%20to%20providing%20MCLI%20translators%20with%20the%20level%20of%20editorial%20support%20that%20they%20need%20and%20deserve%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said%20in%20an%20email%20to%20%3Cem%3EThe%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3EWire%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F06085544%2FUntitled-design-5-1024x576.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22840%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F06085544%2FUntitled-design-5-1024x576.jpg%201024w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F06085544%2FUntitled-design-5-300x169.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F06085544%2FUntitled-design-5.jpg%201200w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-700320%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22473%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EBooks%20published%20by%20the%20MCLI%E2%80%99s%20translators.%20Photo%3A%20Official%20Instagram%20account.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EKrishnan%20is%20a%20Chennai-based%20editor%20while%20Hoskote%20is%20an%20internationally%20renowned%20art%20curator%20and%20poet%20from%20Mumbai.%20He%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fm.thewire.in%2Farticle%2Fthe%2Fcurator-ranjit-hoskote-resigns-from-documentas-finding-committee-over-anti-semitism-allegations%2Famp%5C%22%3Ewas%20in%20the%20news%20a%20few%20months%20ago%3C%2Fa%3E%20when%20his%20criticism%20of%20Hindutva%20and%20Zionism%20and%20an%20earlier%20call%20for%20the%20boycott%20of%20Israel%20prompted%20the%20German%20government%20to%20threaten%20withdrawal%20of%20financial%20support%20from%20the%20%E2%80%98Documenta%E2%80%99%20art%20event%20unless%20it%20ended%20its%20association%20with%20him.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20joint%20statement%20by%20the%20preeminent%20editors%20of%20MCLI%20is%20shocking.%20I%20am%20personally%20aware%20of%20the%20hard%20work%20put%20in%20by%20the%20editors.%20MCLI%20was%20looking%20to%20establish%20itself%20as%20the%20most%20important%20translational%20effort%20to%20showcase%20the%20riches%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20multilingual%20literary%20cultures.%20I%20am%20sharing%20the%20pained%20statement%20of%20the%20editors.%20In%20solidarity%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20founding%20editor%20of%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20Sidharth%20Bhatia.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EPast%20controversy%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EPollock%20and%20his%20work%20done%20in%20association%20with%20the%20library%20came%20into%20focus%20in%202016%20after%20a%20petition%20signed%20by%20Hindutva-influenced%20academics%20demanded%20his%20removal%20from%20the%20library%E2%80%99s%20editorship.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20petition%20said%20that%20Pollock%20%E2%80%9Chas%20deep%20antipathy%20towards%20many%20of%20the%20ideals%20and%20values%20cherished%20and%20practiced%20in%20our%20civilisation.%E2%80%9D%20It%20said%20that%20for%20a%20project%20of%20this%20magnitude%2C%20we%20need%20a%20%E2%80%9Cteam%20of%20scholars%20who%20not%20only%20have%20proven%20mastery%20in%20the%20relevant%20Indian%20languages%20but%20are%20also%20deeply%20rooted%20and%20steeped%20in%20the%20intellectual%20traditions%20of%20India.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20may%20be%20noted%20that%20Pollock%20is%20a%20very%20renowned%20scholar%20and%20authority%20in%20his%20field.%20He%20is%20the%20Arvind%20Raghunathan%20Professor%20of%20South%20Asian%20studies%20at%20Columbia%20University.%20He%20also%20served%20as%20the%20William%20B.%20Ransford%20Professor%20of%20Sanskrit%20and%20Indian%20Studies%20at%20Columbia%2C%20and%20before%20that%20as%20the%20George%20V.%20Bobrinskoy%20Distinguished%20Service%20Professor%20of%20Sanskrit%20and%20Indic%20Studies%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Chicago.%20Pollock%20also%20holds%20a%20Masters%20(1973)%20and%20PhD%20(1975)%20in%20Sanskrit%20and%20Indian%20Studies.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20addition%20to%20questioning%20Pollock%E2%80%99s%20credentials%2C%20the%20petition%2C%20largely%20dismissed%20as%20trivial%20by%20notable%20scholars%20and%20journalists%2C%20also%20objected%20to%20his%20support%20of%20the%202016%20protests%20at%20the%20Jawaharlal%20Nehru%20University%2C%20saying%20that%20%E2%80%9Che%20has%20shown%20disrespect%20for%20the%20integrity%20of%20India%E2%80%9D.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EPollock%20was%20one%20of%20the%20several%20eminent%20signatories%20for%20a%20statement%20expressing%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.washingtonpost.com%2Fworld%2Fasia_pacific%2Fprotests-spread-across-india-against-students-arrest-for-sedition%2F2016%2F02%2F18%2F296a5861-ae47-4209-b7cf-3956bc62fc16_story.html%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9Cheartfelt%20solidarity%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20with%20JNU%20students%20who%20had%20been%20accused%20of%20carrying%20out%20%E2%80%9Canti-national%E2%80%9D%20activities%20on%20campus.%20The%20statement%20also%20condemned%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20culture%20of%20authoritarian%20menace%20that%20the%20present%20government%20in%20India%20has%20generated%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%E2%80%99s%20pretty%20clear%20the%20petitioners%20haven%E2%80%99t%20read%20any%20of%20the%20Murty%20Library%20publications%2C%20or%20if%20they%20did%2C%20didn%E2%80%99t%20find%20anything%20to%20complain%20about%2C%20author%20and%20journalist%20Raghu%20Karnad%20had%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Farticle%2Fbeyond-business%2Fproject-interrupted-116031101266_1.html%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Etold%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EBusiness%20Standard%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3Ein%202016.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CSo%2C%20the%20petition%20is%20completely%20trivial%20on%20the%20matter%20of%20scholarship%2C%20which%20is%20what%20made%20me%20wonder%20about%20the%20petitioners%20themselves.%20Let%E2%80%99s%20just%20say%20I%20was%20amused%20but%20I%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20surprised%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIntellectuals%20had%20also%20accused%20the%20petitioners%20of%20quoting%20Pollock%20selectively%20and%20out%20of%20context%2C%20with%20some%20like%20Ramachandra%20Guha%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Findia%2Fpollock-murty-classical-library-issue-indian-experts-back-canadian-prof%2Fstory-jeaEJlPwycQZBZIRUlarjI.html%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ecalling%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20it%20%E2%80%9Cfrivolous%20and%20motivated%E2%80%9D%2C%20and%20Kancha%20Ilaiah%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindu