acies%20involved%20in%20setting%20up%20a%20business%20from%20scratch%2C%20especially%20one%20that%20is%20very%20laborious%20and%20customer-centric.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20worried%20if%20this%20hair%20oil%20would%20work%20on%20everyone.%20My%20idea%20was%20to%20help%20people%20manage%20hair%20fall.%20I%20never%20thought%20of%20doing%20a%20business%20and%20was%20unsure%20of%20facing%20everyting%20that%20it%20involved%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20shares%20candidly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20mother-in-law%20stood%20by%20her%20like%20a%20rock%20and%20defied%20her%20age%20to%20literally%20burn%20the%20midnight%20oil.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20win%20for%20the%20duo%20was%20successfully%20fulfilling%20the%20100%20orders.%20From%20that%20day%20on%2C%20there%20has%20been%20no%20looking%20back.%20The%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F334496%2Fkashmir-rukhsaar-sayeed-masterchef-india-chef-khalis-frozen-foods%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etwo-woman%20show%3C%2Fa%3E%20worked%20day%20and%20night%20to%20make%20the%20oil.%20Till%20September%202023%2C%20they%20made%20the%20oil%20at%20home%20and%20managed%20manufacturing%2C%20packaging%2C%20customer%20support%2C%20social%20media%2C%20and%20website%20all%20by%20themselves.%20After%20the%20success%20of%20their%20oil%2C%20they%20introduced%20a%20shampoo%20using%20Rajni%E2%80%99s%20recipe%2C%20a%20conditioner%2C%20scalp%20scrub%20and%20comb.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20they%20have%20over%208%2C000%20orders%20per%20month.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EWhat%E2%80%99s%20the%20secret%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20938px)%20100vw%2C%20938px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fnidhi2-1709647312.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22938%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Nidhi's%20Grandma%20Secret%20operates%20out%20of%20a%20manufacturing%20facility%20in%20Panchkula%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fnidhi2-1709647312.jpeg%20938w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fnidhi2-1709647312-176x300.jpeg%20176w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fnidhi2-1709647312-500x853.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fnidhi2-1709647312-768x1310.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fnidhi2-1709647312-900x1536.jpeg%20900w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fnidhi2-1709647312-150x256.jpeg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-343996%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221600%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ENidhi%E2%80%99s%20Grandma%20Secret%20operates%20out%20of%20a%20manufacturing%20facility%20in%20Panchkula%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20makes%20this%20oil%20sell%20out%20and%20attract%20repeat%20customers%3F%20Nidhi%20states%20that%20it%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%98100%20percent%20natural%20and%20homemade%E2%80%99.%20The%20oil%20is%20made%20using%20a%20secret%20mix%20of%2013%20herbs%20with%20coconut%20oil%20as%20the%20base.%20Without%20revealing%20the%20secret%2C%20here%E2%80%99s%20what%20Nidhi%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20make%20the%20oil%20in%20an%20iron%20kadhai%2C%20add%20coconut%20oil%2C%20and%20add%20each%20of%20the%20ingredients%20one%20by%20one.%20We%20cook%20it%20for%20at%20least%20two%20hours%20after%20which%20we%20rest%20it%20for%208-10%20hours.%20The%20next%20morning%2C%20we%20strain%20it%20using%20a%20cotton%20cloth%20and%20reheat%20it.%20It%E2%80%99s%20then%20cooled%2C%20strained%20and%20packed%2C%E2%80%9D%20explains%20Nidhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ingredients%20include%20curry%20leaf%20and%20aloe%20vera%20gel%20among%20others.%20They%20make%20about%20100%20litr