%2C%20Mandala%20drawing%2C%20and%20handmade%20recycled%20paper%2C%20along%20with%20cookery%20classes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20also%20have%20guided%20excursions%20to%20explore%20Shekhawati%E2%80%99s%20unique%20heritage%2C%20countryside%20outings%20such%20as%20bicycle%20tours%20and%20camel%20cart%20strolls%2C%20and%20live%20music%20programs%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ESustainability%20at%20its%20very%20core%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202013%2C%20Apani%20Dhani%20Ecolodge%20won%20the%20Responsible%20Tourism%20Award%20from%20Wild%20Asia%20in%20the%20category%20Best%20in%20Cultural%20Preservation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-captioned%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCqc91JiPkH7%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCqc91JiPkH7%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3EView%20this%20post%20on%20Instagram%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCqc91JiPkH7%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EA%20post%20shared%20by%20Shekhawati%20(Nawalgarh)%20%E2%80%93%20Rajasthan%20(%40apanidhani_ecolodge)%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%20%5Cn%3Cp%3EExplaining%20how%20the%20building%20in%20itself%20embodies%20sustainability%2C%20Ramesh%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20initially%20used%20locally-acquired%20clay%20for%20the%20walls%20and%20pampas%20grass%20for%20the%20roofs%20in%20our%20initial%20huts%2C%20while%20our%20yoga%20hall%2C%20dining%20room%2C%20and%20family%20room%20feature%20rammed%20earth%20walls.%20For%20the%20two%20new%20rooms%20constructed%20during%20the%20Covid-19%20pandemic%2C%20we%20utilised%20AAC%20blocks%20for%20the%20walls%20and%20stone%20slabs%20for%20the%20roofs.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBesides%2C%20the%20eco-stay%20follows%20a%20plethora%20of%20sustainable%20practices%20to%20keep%20the%20nature%20around%20it%20intact.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CMy%20commitment%20to%20ecotourism%20and%20sustainable%20travel%20predates%20its%20global%20buzzword%20status.%20Sustainable%2C%20environmentally-friendly%20practices%20have%20long%20been%20ingrained%20in%20our%20daily%20operations.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20guests%20are%20guided%20towards%20sustainable%20personal%20use%20of%20water%20resources%20in%20our%20semi-arid%20environment%2C%20with%20practices%20such%20as%20rainwater%20harvesting%20implemented%20at%20the%20stay.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBesides%20using%20photovoltaic%20panels%20and%20solar%20water%20heaters%2C%20all%20the%20meals%20are%20served%20in%20disposable%20and%20compostable%20leaf%20plates%2C%20and%20we%20offer%20a%20sustainable%20and%20responsible%20laundry%20service%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdditionally%2C%20they%20compost%20all%20their%20wet%20waste%20which%20is%20later%20used%20in%20their%20fields.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAll%20the%20food%20that%20our%20guests%20eat%20is%20sourced%20from%20our%20organic%20fields%2C%20which%20cultivate%20vegetables%2C%20cereals%2C%20pulses%2C%20oilseeds%2C%20and%20more.%20We%20refrain%20from%20using%20c